question.text: Saya ingin tahu mengapa kemenangan 4D saya belum masuk ke dalam wallet.
variations: Kenapa kemenangan saya belum masuk?
Adakah kemenangan saya akan masuk?
Bila kemenangan 4D saya akan diterima?

languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu mengapa kemenangan 4D saya belum masuk ke dalam wallet.

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings have not been credited yet, it usually takes between 5 to 30 minutes to process. If it still hasn't appeared after that time, please wait a moment or contact support with your transaction details. Additionally, if you have a 4D win, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet, so check the app periodically. If it has been more than 30 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, please reach out to us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum masuk, biasanya ia akan diproses dalam masa 5 hingga 30 minit. Jika selepas itu masih tiada, sila tunggu sekejap atau hubungi sokongan langsung dengan butiran transaksi anda. Jika ada nombor 4D kena, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet secara automatik, sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam app. Jika lebih 30 minit masih belum masuk, boleh roger kami semula dengan screenshot resit & result.

question.text: Why is there a delay in the payout process for my winnings?
variations: Kenapa lewat payout boss?
Why is my payout taking so long?

languages.en: Why is there a delay in the payout process for my winnings?
languages.ms: Kenapa lewat payout boss?

detailed.en: Payout delays are usually caused by the system processing being slower than usual. If your winnings have not been credited within 1-10 minutes, please be patient as the system is processing your transaction. If it takes longer than expected, feel free to contact our live chat support for further clarification. If you win with iBox Super 5048, your winnings should be credited automatically. Please check the 'Report' section for updates on your winnings. If there are any issues or if it does not appear, do not hesitate to contact us for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Kelewatan payout biasanya disebabkan oleh proses sistem yang mungkin lebih lambat dari biasa. Jika kemenangan anda belum dikreditkan dalam masa 1-10 minit, sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses transaksi anda. Jika ia mengambil masa lebih lama dari yang dijangkakan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk penjelasan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I have issues logging in after topping up my account?

languages.en: What should I do if I have issues logging in after topping up my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya mempunyai masalah untuk masuk selepas menambah nilai akaun saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, once you have topped up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it still hasn't appeared after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, setelah anda menambah nilai, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit ke halaman tambah nilai dalam aplikasi. Setelah memuat naik, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia masih belum muncul selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk pengesahan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: After topping up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds will be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, dana akan dikreditkan dalam masa 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan dana belum dikreditkan, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: I have uploaded the receipt, can you please confirm the status of my top-up?
variations: Is my top-up processed after uploading the receipt?
How long does it take for the top-up to reflect after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: I have uploaded the receipt, can you please confirm the status of my top-up?
languages.ms: Saya telah memuat naik resit, bolehkah anda mengesahkan status top-up saya?

detailed.en: Once you have uploaded the receipt, please wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process your top-up. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, please respond in live chat for further assistance. Good luck and may you have many wins!
detailed.ms: Setelah anda memuat naik resit, sila tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses top-up anda. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum dikreditkan, sila balas di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya dan dapat banyak kemenangan!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited to my account?
variations: Top up tak masuk
My top-up hasn't appeared

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If your top-up status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the top-up is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika status top-up anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan top-up masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I have won in Jaguar 3 and haven't seen the credits for my winnings yet?

languages.en: What should I do if I have won in Jaguar 3 and haven't seen the credits for my winnings yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah menang dalam Jaguar 3 dan belum melihat kredit untuk kemenangan saya?

detailed.en: If you have won in Jaguar 3, your winnings from J2/J3 will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credits. Thank you for your patience, and may you have great luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menang dalam Jaguar 3, kemenangan J2/J3 akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda mendapat HUAT yang besar!

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been received after topping up?
variations: kredit belum masuk
sudah topup

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been received after topping up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya belum diterima selepas top-up?

detailed.en: If your credit has not been received after topping up, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes for the confirmation. If the credit still does not appear after that, please send your receipt via live chat for further assistance. If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it takes more than 10 minutes, you can send a message to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika kredit anda belum diterima selepas top-up, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika kredit masih belum masuk selepas itu, sila hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika status menunjukkan PENDING, maksudnya sistem tengah proses sekarang. Mohon tunggu sampai sistem selesai proses. Jangan upload resit banyak kali, sebab akan buat proses jadi lambat. Jika lebih 10 minit belum selesai, boleh hantar ke live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: Why hasn't my winnings been credited yet?
variations: Duit win belum masuk lagi ka bos

languages.en: Why hasn't my winnings been credited yet?
languages.ms: Duit win belum masuk lagi ka bos

detailed.en: If your winnings have not been credited yet, it usually takes between 5 to 30 minutes for the amount to be credited automatically. If it has been longer than that and you still do not see it, please be patient or contact our live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum masuk, biasanya ia akan dikreditkan secara automatik dalam masa 5 hingga 30 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu dan masih belum muncul, sabar sekejap atau hubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I submitted the wrong amount?
variations: I made a mistake in my submission
How can I correct my submission?

languages.en: What should I do if I submitted the wrong amount?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghantar jumlah yang salah?

detailed.en: You need to submit the correct amount. Previously, you submitted RM25, but you should submit RM24. Please resubmit the correct amount.
detailed.ms: Anda perlu menghantar jumlah yang betul. Sebelum ini, anda menghantar RM25, tetapi anda perlu menghantar RM24. Sila hantar semula jumlah yang betul.

question.text: What should I do if my J3 winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
variations: What happens if my J3 winnings are not showing up?
How long does it take for J3 winnings to be credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my J3 winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan J3 saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If you have won J3, the winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Reports' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have great luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menang J3, kemenangan tersebut akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda dapat HUAT yang besar!

question.text: What should I do if my deposit status is showing as PENDING?
variations: Why is my deposit taking so long?
What does PENDING status mean for my deposit?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit status is showing as PENDING?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status deposit saya menunjukkan PENDING?

detailed.en: If your deposit status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it may slow down the process. If it takes more than 10 minutes, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika status deposit anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia boleh melambatkan proses. Jika ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Why hasn't my winnings from the J3 game been credited to my account yet?
variations: mana Duit kena j23 tak masuk2

languages.en: Why hasn't my winnings from the J3 game been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: mana Duit kena j23 tak masuk2

detailed.en: If your 4D number wins, the system will automatically credit the winnings to your wallet shortly. You can check the results by opening the JOKER app, tapping the 4D icon, selecting the Results menu, and comparing the numbers with your receipt. If there are any issues or delays, you can send your receipt and results to us for verification.
detailed.ms: Kalau nombor 4D anda kena, sistem akan auto masuk duit menang ke wallet dalam masa yang singkat. Anda boleh semak keputusan dengan membuka aplikasi JOKER, tekan ikon 4D, pilih menu Keputusan, dan bandingkan nombor dengan resit anda. Jika ada masalah atau lambat masuk, anda boleh hantar resit dan keputusan kepada kami untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal status shows PENDING?
variations: What does it mean if my withdrawal is still pending?
How long should I wait for my withdrawal to be processed?

languages.en: What should I do if my withdrawal status shows PENDING?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status pengeluaran saya menunjukkan PENDING?

detailed.en: If your withdrawal status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still pending, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status pengeluaran anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What are the chances of winning in a lottery or 4D game?

languages.en: What are the chances of winning in a lottery or 4D game?
languages.ms: Apakah peluang untuk menang dalam permainan loteri atau 4D?

detailed.en: Winning in a lottery or 4D game can be quite challenging due to the low odds of hitting the jackpot. However, many players enjoy the thrill and excitement of participating, and there are often smaller prizes available as well.
detailed.ms: Menang dalam loteri atau permainan 4D boleh menjadi agak mencabar kerana peluang yang rendah untuk memenangi jackpot. Namun, ramai pemain menikmati keseronokan dan kegembiraan menyertai, dan sering terdapat hadiah yang lebih kecil juga.

question.text: What should I do if my payment via Fast Payment (FPX) has not been processed after 10 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment via Fast Payment (FPX) has not been processed after 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pembayaran saya melalui Fast Payment (FPX) belum diproses selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: After topping up via Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the payment should be completed within 1-10 minutes. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup melalui Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, pembayaran akan diselesaikan dalam 1-10 minit. Jika ia belum diproses selepas 10 minit, sila hantarkan resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: Why hasn't my deposit of RM15 been credited yet?
variations: kenapa deposit x masuk lgi

languages.en: Why hasn't my deposit of RM15 been credited yet?
languages.ms: kenapa deposit x masuk lgi

detailed.en: If your deposit of RM15 has not been credited, there may be a technical issue or an error with the transaction method. If the money has been deducted from your account but the deposit has not been successful, try making the deposit again or send the receipt via live chat for further verification. Don't worry, we will help resolve this issue!
detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM15 tidak masuk, mungkin ada masalah teknikal atau kesilapan dengan kaedah transaksi. Jika duit sudah ditolak dari akaun tetapi deposit tidak berjaya, cuba buat deposit semula atau hantar resit melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Jangan risau, kita akan bantu selesaikan masalah ini!

question.text: Why am I not getting any points in the game despite playing multiple spins?
variations: Why is the game not giving me points?
What is wrong with the game that I'm not winning?

languages.en: Why am I not getting any points in the game despite playing multiple spins?
languages.ms: Mengapa saya tidak mendapat sebarang mata dalam permainan walaupun bermain banyak pusingan?

detailed.en: I understand your frustration. Sometimes luck is not on our side. Don't give up, as fortune can come at any time! The key is to enjoy the game and try again calmly. I wish you good luck and hope you hit big in the next round!
detailed.ms: Saya faham perasaan anda. Kadang-kadang nasib tidak menyebelahi kita. Jangan putus asa, rezeki boleh datang bila-bila masa! Kunci adalah untuk menikmati permainan dan cuba lagi dengan tenang. Saya doakan anda banyak nasib baik dan dapat HUAT besar dalam pusingan seterusnya!

question.text: What should I do if my deposit has not been credited to my account?
variations: depo belum in
my deposit hasn't arrived yet

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit has not been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your deposit of RM15 has not been credited, please wait around 3-10 minutes after uploading the receipt. If it still does not appear in your wallet, you can send a screenshot of the receipt to me, and I will help resolve this issue promptly. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM15 anda belum dikredit, sila tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika masih tiada dalam wallet, boleh hantar tangkapan skrin resit kepada saya, dan saya akan bantu selesaikan masalah ini dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do if I'm not having good luck in my games?

languages.en: What should I do if I'm not having good luck in my games?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak mempunyai nasib baik dalam permainan saya?

detailed.en: Don't give up, as luck can change at any moment! If you win big, you can withdraw a lot! Keep playing patiently!
detailed.ms: Jangan putus asa, sebab keberuntungan boleh berubah bila-bila masa! Jika anda menang besar, anda boleh keluarkan banyak! Teruskan bermain dengan sabar!

question.text: What should I do if the deposit amount does not match the receipt?
variations: What to do if my deposit amount is incorrect?
How can I resolve a discrepancy in my deposit?

languages.en: What should I do if the deposit amount does not match the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika jumlah deposit tidak sepadan dengan resit?

detailed.en: To resolve the issue of the deposit amount not matching the receipt, ensure that the amount entered is exactly as stated on the receipt. If there is a discrepancy, such as 'missing one number', please check the transaction details in your banking app. If the problem persists, contact customer support with a screenshot of your transaction for further investigation. If anything is unclear, let me know!
detailed.ms: Untuk menyelesaikan masalah jumlah deposit yang tidak sepadan dengan resit, pastikan jumlah yang dimasukkan adalah tepat seperti yang tertera pada resit. Jika ada perbezaan, seperti 'kurang satu nombor', sila semak butiran transaksi dalam aplikasi perbankan anda. Jika masalah masih berterusan, hubungi sokongan pelanggan dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk siasatan lanjut. Jika ada yang tidak jelas, beritahu saya!

question.text: What is the process for winnings to be credited to my wallet after a bet?

languages.en: What is the process for winnings to be credited to my wallet after a bet?
languages.ms: Apakah proses untuk kemenangan dikreditkan ke dalam wallet saya selepas bertaruh?

detailed.en: Hi boss, winnings from football bets will be credited to your wallet automatically within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it has not been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Salam boss, kemenangan pertaruhan bola akan dikreditkan ke wallet anda secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Mohon bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Jika masih belum dikreditkan selepas 24 jam, anda boleh menghubungi kami melalui live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
variations: topup
ATM top up process
how to top up using ATM

languages.en: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya menggunakan ATM?

detailed.en:
To top up using an ATM, follow these steps:

1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers.
2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu.
3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).
4. Enter the top-up amount (Minimum RM10).
5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt.
6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat.
7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes.

Make sure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection.
If you have any issues or need assistance, please reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini:

1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank.
2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'.
3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi).
4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10).
5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit.
6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat.
7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit.

Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan.
Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kami dalam live chat ya!

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been processed yet?
variations: betul masuk kredit lg

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been processed yet?
languages.ms: betul masuk kredit lg

detailed.en: If the money is delayed in being credited, it usually takes between 1 to 10 minutes to process. If it has been longer than that, you may want to check your receipt or contact us via live chat for further assistance. Don't worry, we are here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika duit lambat masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa antara 1 hingga 10 minit untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih dari itu, mungkin anda boleh semak semula resit atau hubungi kami melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jangan risau, kami di sini untuk membantu!

question.text: Can you help me check why I haven't been able to log in yet?

languages.en: Can you help me check why I haven't been able to log in yet?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda bantu saya semak mengapa saya belum dapat log masuk?

detailed.en: If you are having trouble logging in, you can try the following steps: 1. Make sure your username and password are correct. 2. Try resetting your password if you have forgotten it. 3. Check your internet connection. 4. If you still cannot log in, try logging in from a different device or browser. If there is anything else I can assist you with, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Pastikan nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda betul. 2. Cuba untuk menetapkan semula kata laluan jika anda terlupa. 3. Periksa sambungan internet anda. 4. Jika masih tidak dapat, cuba log masuk dari peranti atau pelayar lain. Kalau ada apa-apa lagi yang saya boleh bantu, beritahu saja ya!

question.text: What should I do if I have won a 4D lottery but the winnings have not yet been credited to my wallet?

languages.en: What should I do if I have won a 4D lottery but the winnings have not yet been credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah menang loteri 4D tetapi kemenangan belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If your 4D number wins, the system will automatically credit the winnings to your wallet shortly. To check the 4D results, open the JOKER App, tap on the 4D icon, select the Results menu, and compare the numbers and house with your receipt. If there are any issues or delays in the crediting process, you can send your receipt and results to us for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika nombor 4D anda menang, sistem akan secara automatik mengkreditkan kemenangan ke dalam dompet anda dalam masa yang singkat. Untuk menyemak keputusan 4D, buka Aplikasi JOKER, tekan ikon 4D, pilih menu Keputusan, dan bandingkan nombor dan rumah dengan resit anda. Jika ada sebarang masalah atau kelewatan dalam proses pengkreditan, anda boleh menghantar resit dan keputusan anda kepada kami untuk pengesahan.

question.text: What should I do if I don't see the credit in my account after topping up iBox?
variations: What happens if the credit doesn't appear?
How long does it take for the iBox credit to show up?

languages.en: What should I do if I don't see the credit in my account after topping up iBox?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak melihat kredit dalam akaun selepas top-up iBox?

detailed.en: After topping up iBox, it usually takes 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If you still do not see the credit in your account after this period, please check your wallet or send a screenshot of the receipt via live chat. The winnings from Jaguar at 9 PM will be credited automatically to your wallet. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for updates. If there are any issues, feel free to contact live chat.
detailed.ms: Selepas top-up iBox, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika anda masih tidak melihat kredit dalam akaun selepas tempoh ini, sila semak dompet anda atau hantar tangkapan skrin resit melalui live chat. Kemenangan dari Jaguar pada jam 9 malam akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Report' antara jam 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk kemas kini. Jika ada masalah, jangan ragu untuk hubungi live chat.

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my wallet after more than 30 minutes?
variations: What to do if winnings are delayed?
How long does it take for winnings to appear in my wallet?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my wallet after more than 30 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya selepas lebih dari 30 minit?

detailed.en: If it has been more than 30 minutes and your winnings have still not been credited, please check the transaction in the app first. If there is nothing, I recommend sending the transaction details through live chat so we can assist you in checking it immediately. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika tiada apa-apa, saya sarankan untuk menghantar butiran transaksi melalui live chat supaya kami dapat membantu menyemak dengan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: How long does it take for credit to be processed and entered into my account?
variations: Lama credit nak masuk
Lebih 10minit la tu

languages.en: How long does it take for credit to be processed and entered into my account?
languages.ms: Lama credit nak masuk

detailed.en: If your credit or top-up is delayed, it usually takes between 5 to 30 minutes. If it has been more than that and it still hasn't been processed, please send a screenshot of your transaction receipt via live chat for assistance. If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can send it to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan atau top-up anda lambat masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa antara 5 hingga 30 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu dan masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit transaksi anda melalui live chat untuk kami bantu selesaikan. Jika status tunjuk PENDING, maksudnya sistem tengah proses sekarang ya. Mohon boss tunggu dulu sampai sistem selesai proses. Jangan upload resit banyak kali, sebab akan buat proses jadi lambat. Kalau lebih 10 minit belum selesai, boleh hantar ke live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do if my betting winnings haven't been credited to my wallet yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my betting winnings haven't been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan pertaruhan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, the betting winnings will be credited to your wallet automatically within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it still hasn't been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, kemenangan pertaruhan akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Jika ia masih belum dikreditkan selepas 24 jam, anda boleh menghubungi kami melalui live chat untuk pengesahan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited after 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of the receipt you uploaded. I will check it for you immediately. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit yang anda muat naik. Saya akan semak dengan segera untuk anda! Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: How can my friend join the Jokers? Please send the link.

languages.en: How can my friend join the Jokers? Please send the link.
languages.ms: Bagaimana kawan saya boleh sertai Jokers? Sila hantar pautan.

detailed.en: To register, your friend should follow these steps: 1. Go to 'Profile' in the app. 2. Copy the 'Referral Link' found in your profile. 3. Send that link to your friend for registration. 4. Your friend can use that link to register and start playing. The Referral Link is only available in your own account within the app. If there are any issues or if assistance is needed, please contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk mendaftar, kawan anda perlu mengikuti langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke 'Profile' dalam aplikasi. 2. Salin 'Referral Link' yang terdapat dalam profil anda. 3. Hantar pautan tersebut kepada kawan anda untuk pendaftaran. 4. Kawan anda boleh menggunakan pautan tersebut untuk mendaftar dan mula bermain. Pautan Referral hanya boleh didapati dalam akaun anda sendiri dalam aplikasi. Jika ada sebarang masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat.

question.text: How long does it take for a credit to be reflected in my account after making a deposit?

languages.en: How long does it take for a credit to be reflected in my account after making a deposit?
languages.ms: Berapa lama masa yang diambil untuk kredit dipantulkan dalam akaun saya selepas membuat deposit?

detailed.en: If you have made a deposit of RM15 and it has not been credited to your wallet, please check the transaction receipt that you uploaded. Sometimes, deposits may experience delays due to certain terms or conditions. If you have checked and are still facing issues, please contact our customer support for further assistance. I hope this issue can be resolved quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat deposit RM15 dan ia belum dikredit ke dalam wallet, sila semak semula resit transaksi yang telah dimuat naik. Kadang-kadang, deposit mungkin mengalami kelewatan disebabkan oleh terma atau syarat tertentu. Jika anda sudah semak dan masih menghadapi masalah, sila hubungi sokongan pelanggan kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga masalah ini dapat diselesaikan segera!

question.text: What should I do if my upload has not been processed after waiting for a while?

languages.en: What should I do if my upload has not been processed after waiting for a while?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika muat naik saya masih belum diproses?

detailed.en: If it has been more than 10 minutes and your upload is still not processed, please send a screenshot of the receipt and I will investigate it immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan muat naik anda masih belum diproses, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit dan saya akan siasat dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up of RM70 has not been credited yet?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up RM70 saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes after uploading your receipt. If the funds still do not appear, please contact live chat support with your complete receipt for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit selepas memuat naik resit anda. Jika dana masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my winnings from the 9pm Jaguar bet have not been credited to my account?
variations: What if my payout hasn't been credited?
How long does it take for the payout to be credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings from the 9pm Jaguar bet have not been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya dari pertaruhan Jaguar 9pm belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your winnings from the 9pm Jaguar bet have not been credited, it usually gets credited automatically to your wallet. Please check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for confirmation. If your winnings still haven't been credited after that time, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan bet Jaguar 9pm anda belum dikreditkan, biasanya ia akan masuk secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila semak bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM dan 10:30 PM untuk pengesahan. Jika selepas waktu tersebut kemenangan anda masih belum masuk, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: I won the second prize at 9 PM, but why hasn't the money been credited to my account yet?

languages.en: I won the second prize at 9 PM, but why hasn't the money been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Saya menang hadiah kedua pada jam 9 malam, tetapi mengapa wang itu belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: The winnings for J2 and J3 will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit.
detailed.ms: Kemenangan untuk J2 dan J3 akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut.

question.text: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa maksudnya apabila status menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?

detailed.en: When the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Apabila status menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit berulang kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Can the 90 amount be credited to the wallet, and how does the deposit and bonus system work?

How does the deposit and bonus system work?

languages.en: Can the 90 amount be credited to the wallet, and how does the deposit and bonus system work?

Bagaimana jika saya tidak menerima wang yang telah dihantar?

question.text: I mistakenly uploaded the wrong receipt for my top-up. What should I do?

What to do if I made a mistake with my receipt?

languages.en: I mistakenly uploaded the wrong receipt for my top-up. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya silap muat naik resit untuk top-up saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have submitted two receipts for the top-up, the system only requires one receipt for verification. Make sure not to upload the same receipt twice, as it may be rejected. Please wait 3-10 minutes for processing. If there are any issues, feel free to reply to us in the live chat.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menghantar dua resit untuk top-up, sistem hanya memerlukan satu resit untuk semakan. Pastikan untuk tidak mengupload resit yang sama dua kali, kerana ia mungkin akan ditolak. Sila tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pemprosesan. Jika ada sebarang masalah, jangan ragu untuk balas kepada kami dalam live chat.

question.text: Apakah status pengkreditan dana untuk resit 9909 yang saya hantar?

languages.ms: Apakah status pengkreditan dana untuk resit 9909 yang saya hantar?

detailed.ms: Kemenangan 4D akan dikreditkan ke wallet JOKER secara automatik. Mohon bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses.

question.text: How long does it take for my winnings to be credited to my wallet after winning in J3?
variations: What is the process for receiving my J3 winnings?
When will my J3 winnings appear in my wallet?

languages.en: How long does it take for my winnings to be credited to my wallet after winning in J3?
languages.ms: Berapa lama masa yang diambil untuk kemenangan saya dikreditkan ke dalam dompet selepas menang di J3?

detailed.en: Your J3 winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have a big win!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan J3 anda akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet secara automatik. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda dapat kemenangan besar!

question.text: What should I do if I mistakenly banked into the wrong account number?
variations: I made a mistake with my bank transfer.
I accidentally sent money to the wrong account.

languages.en: What should I do if I mistakenly banked into the wrong account number?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah bank ke nombor akaun yang salah?

detailed.en: If you have transferred to your old bank account, unfortunately, the money cannot be refunded. However, you can still use the credited amount to play. You should ensure to top-up correctly by uploading your bank-in receipt through (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). After submission, wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not appear within 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah transfer ke akaun bank lama anda, malangnya, duit tersebut tidak dapat dipulangkan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan amaun yang telah dikreditkan untuk bermain. Pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul dengan memuat naik resit bank-in anda melalui (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). Selepas penghantaran, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika kredit tidak muncul dalam masa 10 minit, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally entered the wrong bank account for a transfer?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally entered the wrong bank account for a transfer?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah masukkan akaun bank untuk pemindahan?

detailed.en: If you accidentally transferred to your own bank account, the funds cannot be returned. However, you can still use the credited amount for gaming. Make sure to top-up correctly by uploading the bank-in slip through (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). After submission, wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not arrive within 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tersalah transfer ke akaun bank sendiri, wang tersebut tidak dapat dikembalikan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan jumlah yang telah dikreditkan untuk permainan. Pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul dengan memuat naik slip bank-in melalui (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). Selepas penghantaran, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika kredit tidak tiba dalam 10 minit, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: I am experiencing issues with Maybank transactions. Can you help me understand what the problem might be?
variations: maybank problem
maybank resistance Kelmarsh...ada problem....u fahamkah

languages.en: I am experiencing issues with Maybank transactions. Can you help me understand what the problem might be?

detailed.en: If there is an issue with Maybank transactions, it could be due to maintenance or system disruptions. I recommend checking the official Maybank website for the latest information regarding any ongoing issues.

question.text: Di mana saya boleh mengetahui tentang pembayaran cepat?

languages.en: Where can I find information about fast payments?
languages.ms: Di mana saya boleh mengetahui tentang pembayaran cepat?

detailed.en: To check your transaction history for top-ups and withdrawals, follow these steps: Open the Joker app, tap the wallet icon at the bottom center, select 'Transaction History', choose the date, and press Search to view all incoming/outgoing records. If you still can't find it, please take a screenshot and send it here for assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk semak sejarah transaksi topup & withdraw, ikut langkah-langkah ini: Buka aplikasi Joker, tekan ikon dompet di bawah tengah, pilih 'Transaction History', pilih tarikh dan tekan Search untuk melihat semua rekod masuk/keluar. Jika masih tidak jumpa, sila ambil tangkapan skrin dan hantar di sini untuk bantuan.

question.text: What time will the boss bonus win be available?
variations: boss bonus win pukul brqpa

languages.en: What time will the boss bonus win be available?
languages.ms: Pukul berapa angpau boss akan tersedia?

detailed.en: If you have a winning 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little time today. The winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please check the app from time to time.
detailed.ms: Kalau ada nombor 4D kena, mohon boss sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet boss secara automatik. Sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam app.

languages.en: Is there any money that has not been credited to account 4922 yet?
languages.ms: Adakah duit yang belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun 4922?

detailed.en: The funds you mentioned are currently being processed. If you have resent the receipt, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to be credited to your account. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, please contact live chat for immediate assistance. In the meantime, you will be able to purchase numbers for the 9 PM draw once your funds are credited.

Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum masuk, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Sementara itu, anda akan dapat membeli nombor untuk undian 9 malam setelah dana anda dikreditkan.

question.text: Bagaimana jika kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk dan saya sudah bank in RM33 tetapi masih tiada kemasukan?
variations: Kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk, apa yang perlu saya buat?
Saya sudah bank in tetapi tiada kemasukan, kenapa?

languages.ms: Bagaimana jika kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk dan saya sudah bank in RM33 tetapi masih tiada kemasukan?

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings have not been credited yet, please wait around 10 minutes for the system to process. If it still does not appear, contact live chat with your transaction details. If you have already banked in RM33 but it still hasn't been credited, there might be a slight delay. Please wait another 10 minutes. If it still does not appear, send a screenshot of the receipt to us via live chat so we can help resolve this issue.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum masuk, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit untuk sistem memproses. Jika masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda. Jika sudah bank in RM33 tetapi masih belum masuk, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan. Sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit lagi. Jika masih tiada, hantar screenshot resit kepada kami melalui live chat supaya kami boleh bantu selesaikan masalah ini.

question.text: User is inquiring about the status of their winnings not being credited yet.

detailed.en: If your winnings have not been credited yet, please wait 10 minutes for the system to process it. If it still does not appear, please contact live chat with your transaction details. If there is a 4D win, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winnings will automatically be credited to your wallet. Please check from time to time in the app. If it has not been credited after 30 minutes, you can contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan anda belum dikredit, sila tunggu 10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda. Jika ada nombor 4D kena, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet anda secara automatik. Sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam app. Jika lebih 30 minit masih belum masuk, boleh roger kami semula dengan screenshot resit & result.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: Saya menghadapi masalah untuk memuat turun aplikasi menggunakan pautan yang diberikan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

languages.ms: Saya menghadapi masalah untuk memuat turun aplikasi menggunakan pautan yang diberikan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.ms:
Jika anda menghadapi masalah dengan pautan yang tidak berfungsi untuk memuat turun, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut:

1. **Salin pautan**: Salin pautan yang diberikan dan tampalkannya ke dalam bar alamat pelayar web anda.
2. **Tekan 'Enter'**: Setelah menampal, tekan 'Enter' untuk memulakan muat turun.
3. **Cuba pelayar lain**: Jika masih tidak berfungsi, cuba gunakan pelayar web yang berbeza.
4. **Semak tetapan pelayar**: Pastikan tiada tetapan yang menghalang muat turun.

Jika anda masih mengalami masalah, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi sokongan sembang langsung kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya! ğŸ˜Š

languages.en: What should I do if my transfer to CIMB is not reflected in my account?

detailed.en: If you have transferred RM33 but it has not appeared in your account, there may be a slight delay. Ensure that you have uploaded the transaction proof in the top-up section of the app. The verification process usually takes 3-10 minutes. If the funds still do not appear after that, please contact live chat with your transaction proof.

Biasanya, proses pengesahan mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika selepas itu masih tiada kemasukan, sila hubungi live chat dengan bukti transaksi.

question.text: Can you confirm if the payment has been successfully processed and if the receipt is the same as the previous one?

languages.en: Can you confirm if the payment has been successfully processed and if the receipt is the same as the previous one?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda mengesahkan jika pembayaran telah diproses dengan jayanya dan jika resit adalah sama seperti yang sebelumnya?

detailed.ms: Ya, resit kali ini adalah sama dengan yang dimuat naik sebelum ini. Sila semak dompet anda untuk mengesahkan pembayaran.

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been deposited into my account after submitting the receipt?

detailed.en: If your funds have not been credited even after you have resubmitted the receipt, it may be under review. Please wait between 3 to 10 minutes for the system to credit your account. If after 10 minutes the funds still have not arrived, please contact live chat for immediate assistance. You will be able to purchase numbers for the 9 PM draw once your account has been credited. Jika selepas 10 minit dana masih belum masuk, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Semoga berjaya!

where can I download Joker?

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited after I uploaded the receipt?
variations: top ul x masuk
top up
what to do if top-up not credited

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited after I uploaded the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya tidak masuk selepas saya muat naik resit?

detailed.en: After you upload the receipt, the system usually takes 3-10 minutes to process the top-up. If the funds still haven't arrived after that period, please check whether you used ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). If you used FPX and it takes more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your transaction via live chat for further verification. Additionally, if you top up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, it should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it still hasn't arrived after 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas anda muat naik resit, biasanya sistem memerlukan 3-10 minit untuk memproses top-up. Jika selepas tempoh itu dana masih belum masuk, sila semak sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Pembayaran Pantas (FPX). Jika menggunakan FPX dan ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, sila hantarkan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda melalui live chat untuk pengesahan lanjut. Selain itu, jika anda top-up menggunakan Pembayaran Pantas (FPX), sila tunggu 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, ia akan masuk dalam 1-10 minit. Jika masih belum masuk selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account yet?
variations: Why hasn't my winning amount been credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you have won a 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little time today. The winning money will be credited to your wallet automatically. Please check from time to time in the app.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang nombor 4D, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses dan mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Duit kemenangan akan dikreditkan ke dalam wallet anda secara automatik. Sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam aplikasi.

question.text: What should I do if I have withdrawn funds and am waiting for my winnings to be credited?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah mengeluarkan dana dan sedang menunggu kemenangan saya dikreditkan?

detailed.ms: Kemenangan 4D akan dikreditkan ke wallet JOKER secara automatik. Mohon bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses.

question.text: What should I do if my bank transfer has not been credited to my account after I deposited RM33?
variations: BoÅŸ saya sudah masuk akaun ni mcm mana?
Dalam kolum sudah xde akaun ni

languages.en: What should I do if my bank transfer has not been credited to my account after I deposited RM33?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pemindahan bank saya belum dikreditkan ke akaun saya selepas saya mendeposit RM33?

detailed.en: If you have banked in RM33 but it has not yet appeared in your account, it usually takes about 3-10 minutes to process. If it still hasn't appeared after 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance. Don't worry, we are here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah bank in RM33, tetapi belum masuk ke akaun, biasanya ia akan mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum masuk, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jangan risau, kami sedia membantu!

question.text: What should I do if my game account is locked and I cannot access it?
variations: Why is my game ID locked?
How can I unlock my game account?

languages.en: What should I do if my game account is locked and I cannot access it?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika ID permainan saya terkunci dan saya tidak dapat mengaksesnya?

detailed.en: If your game account is locked, please wait for the system to process your request. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can send a message to live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika ID permainan anda terkunci, sila tunggu sistem memproses permintaan anda. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghantar mesej ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What are the results of the 4D lottery and how should I celebrate my win?
variations: What should I do after winning the 4D lottery?
How do I celebrate a 4D lottery win?

languages.en: What are the results of the 4D lottery and how should I celebrate my win?
languages.ms: Apakah keputusan loteri 4D dan bagaimana saya harus meraikan kemenangan saya?

detailed.en: Congratulations on your 4D win! Make sure to celebrate your success and enjoy your winnings. Don't forget to take care of your finances and plan for the future!
detailed.ms: Tahniah atas kemenangan 4D anda! Pastikan anda meraikan kejayaan anda dan nikmati kemenangan anda. Jangan lupa untuk menjaga kewangan anda dan merancang untuk masa depan!

question.text: What assistance can I provide you with today?

languages.en: What assistance can I provide you with today?
languages.ms: Apakah bantuan yang boleh saya berikan kepada anda hari ini?

detailed.en: If you have anything else you would like to ask or need help with, don't hesitate to let me know! I hope today is filled with great luck and prosperity!
detailed.ms: Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang ingin ditanya atau perlukan bantuan, jangan segan untuk beritahu ya! Semoga hari ini penuh dengan ONG dan HUAT yang besar!

question.text: What should I do if my bank-in amount is not processed or credited after waiting?
variations: What to do if my top-up is not credited?
How long does it take for the bank-in to be processed?
What if my transaction status shows PENDING?

languages.en: What should I do if my bank-in amount is not processed or credited after waiting?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika jumlah bank-in saya tidak diproses atau dikreditkan selepas menunggu?

detailed.en: If your bank-in amount is not credited after waiting for 10 minutes, please check the transaction in your app. If it still does not appear, upload the transaction receipt via live chat for us to verify. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika dana anda tidak dikreditkan selepas menunggu 10 minit, sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi anda. Jika masih tiada, muat naik resit transaksi melalui live chat untuk kami semak. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if my status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What should I do if my status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status saya menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?

detailed.en: If your status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit berulang kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount and need to upload a new one?

languages.en: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount and need to upload a new one?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah memasukkan jumlah yang salah dan perlu memuat naik yang baru?

detailed.en: If you have entered the wrong amount, please upload it again and write the amount as RM 100. After uploading, wait for 3 to 10 minutes for confirmation. If the money has not yet been credited, please send the receipt via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memasukkan jumlah yang salah, sila muat naik semula dan tulis jumlah sebagai RM 100. Selepas memuat naik, tunggu dalam 3 hingga 10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika duit masih belum masuk, sila hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Can you tell me why the transaction is taking so long?
variations: Why is the transaction slow?
What is causing the delay in my transaction?

languages.en: Can you tell me why the transaction is taking so long?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda beritahu saya mengapa transaksi mengambil masa yang lama?

detailed.en: I understand, boss! If the transaction hasn't gone through yet, could you let me know if you are using ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX)? This will help me check further. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Saya faham, bos! Jika transaksi belum masuk lagi, boleh beritahu saya sama ada bos menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX)? Ini akan membantu saya untuk semak dengan lebih lanjut. Terima kasih!

question.text: Can I withdraw my winnings in cash right now?

languages.en: Can I withdraw my winnings in cash right now?
languages.ms: Boleh withdraw win cash sekarang ka

detailed.en:
To withdraw cash now, follow these steps in the app:

1ï¸âƒ£ Click the 'Wallet' icon (at the bottom center of the screen).

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been processed after 10 minutes?
variations: What to do if my credit is still pending?
How long should I wait for my credit to be processed?

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been processed after 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya belum diproses selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika status menunjukkan PENDING, maksudnya sistem sedang memproses. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What information do I need to provide when making an online transfer using my JOKER ID?

languages.en: What information do I need to provide when making an online transfer using my JOKER ID?
languages.ms: Apakah maklumat yang perlu saya berikan semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian menggunakan ID JOKER saya?

detailed.en: When making an online transfer using your JOKER ID, please ensure to fill in the recipient reference and other payment details. The reference number to use is 17352JKE.
detailed.ms: Semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian menggunakan ID JOKER anda, sila pastikan untuk mengisi rujukan penerima dan butiran pembayaran lain. Nombor rujukan yang perlu digunakan adalah 17352JKE.

question.text: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount during the top-up process?
variations: What to do if I made a mistake in the top-up amount?
How can I correct a wrong top-up amount?

languages.en: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount during the top-up process?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya memasukkan amaun yang salah semasa proses top-up?

detailed.en: If you have entered the wrong amount during the top-up, you need to resend the transaction by uploading the correct receipt. The system will process the updated top-up within 3-10 minutes. If the credit still does not appear, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your receipt for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memasukkan amaun yang salah semasa top-up, anda perlu menghantar semula transaksi dengan memuat naik resit yang betul. Sistem akan memproses top-up yang dikemas kini dalam masa 3-10 minit. Jika kredit masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin resit anda untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if my transaction status is showing as PENDING for more than 10 minutes?
variations: Why is my transaction still pending?
What does it mean if my payment is pending?

languages.en: What should I do if my transaction status is showing as PENDING for more than 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status transaksi saya menunjukkan PENDING lebih dari 10 minit?

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your transaction. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the transaction is still not completed, you can send a message to live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses transaksi anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan transaksi masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghantar mesej ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure it is processed correctly?

languages.en: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure it is processed correctly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya sertakan semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian untuk memastikan ia diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: When making an online transfer, ensure to fill in the 'Recipient Reference' and other payment details accurately. Always include your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' to facilitate quick verification of the receipt.
detailed.ms: Semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian, pastikan untuk mengisi 'Rujukan Penerima' dan butiran pembayaran lain dengan tepat. Sentiasa sertakan ID JOKER anda dalam 'Rujukan Penerima' untuk memudahkan pengesahan resit dengan cepat.

question.text: What should I do if my payment receipt is incomplete or unclear?
variations: What if the receipt I uploaded is not complete?
How can I ensure my payment receipt is clear?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment receipt is incomplete or unclear?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika resit pembayaran saya tidak lengkap atau tidak jelas?

detailed.en: If the receipt you uploaded is incomplete or the information is unclear, make sure the image of the receipt is clear and shows all the necessary details: successful status, amount, date/time, and recipient. If any information is missing, please resend a complete receipt. For further assistance, you can contact our live chat support.
detailed.ms: Jika resit yang anda upload tidak lengkap atau maklumat tidak jelas, pastikan gambar resit tersebut jelas dan menunjukkan semua butiran yang diperlukan: status berjaya, jumlah, tarikh/masa, dan penerima. Jika ada maklumat yang hilang, sila hantar semula resit yang lengkap. Untuk bantuan lanjut, anda boleh hubungi sokongan live chat kami.

question.text: How can I use my own bank account for transactions?
variations: mcm mn boss Sy nk guna bank sendiri
How to use my own bank account?

languages.en: How can I use my own bank account for transactions?
languages.ms: mcm mn boss Sy nk guna bank sendiri

detailed.en: To use your own bank account, you can follow these steps: 1. Open the app and go to the 'Wallet' section. 2. Select 'Top Up'. 3. Enter the amount you wish to add. 4. Upload a clear bank-in slip. 5. Wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the amount does not appear after 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Untuk menggunakan bank sendiri, anda boleh ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka aplikasi dan pergi ke bahagian 'Wallet'. 2. Pilih 'Top Up'. 3. Masukkan jumlah yang ingin ditambah. 4. Muat naik slip bank-in yang jelas. 5. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika selepas 10 minit jumlah tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: Can you please check if my 2D winnings have been credited yet?
variations: Have my 2D winnings been credited?
Is my 2D payout processed?

languages.en: Can you please check if my 2D winnings have been credited yet?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda tolong semak jika kemenangan 2D saya sudah dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If the funds have not been credited even after you have uploaded the receipt, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes. If it still hasn't been credited after that, you can contact live chat for immediate assistance. Also, ensure that you have uploaded the receipt on the top-up page in the app. If you have a 4D win, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet, so please check from time to time in the app.
detailed.ms: Jika dana belum dikredit walaupun anda telah upload resit, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit. Jika selepas itu masih belum masuk, anda boleh hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Pastikan juga anda telah mengupload resit di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Jika anda ada nombor 4D kena, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet anda secara automatik, jadi sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam aplikasi.

question.text: What are the congratulations and best wishes for winning a large amount of money?

languages.en: What are the congratulations and best wishes for winning a large amount of money?
languages.ms: Apakah ucapan tahniah dan harapan terbaik untuk memenangi sejumlah wang yang besar?

detailed.en: Congratulations on your big win! You have successfully transferred RM 15,000. Wishing you more luck and prosperity today! If you have any further questions, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Tahniah atas kemenangan besar anda! Anda telah berjaya memindahkan RM 15,000. Semoga anda mendapat lebih banyak nasib dan kemakmuran hari ini! Jika anda mempunyai sebarang pertanyaan lanjut, jangan ragu untuk bertanya!

question.text: What should I do if I'm having trouble logging in and bonuses are hard to come by?
variations: kasi ong sikiit bos
kasi la ong boss..bonus pun susah masuk

languages.en: What should I do if I'm having trouble logging in and bonuses are hard to come by?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah untuk log masuk dan bonus sukar diperoleh?

detailed.en: I understand, boss! Sometimes luck doesn't favor us. Don't give up, maybe the next round will bring a big win! Keep playing and I hope you get a lot of ONG! ğŸ€ğŸ”¥ If there's anything else, let me know!
detailed.ms: Saya faham, boss! Kadang-kadang nasib memang tak menyebelahi kita. Jangan putus asa, mungkin pusingan seterusnya akan membawa kemenangan besar! Teruskan bermain dan semoga dapat banyak ONG! ğŸ€ğŸ”¥ Jika ada apa-apa lagi, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: What is the status of my J9pm winnings and when will they be credited to my account?

languages.en: What is the status of my J9pm winnings and when will they be credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apakah status kemenangan J9pm saya dan bila ia akan dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: The winnings for J9pm will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit.
detailed.ms: Kemenangan untuk J9pm akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut.

question.text: What assistance can I provide you with today?
variations: dh kah boss
ade ape yang saya boleh bantu

languages.en: What assistance can I provide you with today?
languages.ms: Apa bantuan yang boleh saya berikan kepada anda hari ini?

detailed.en: Huat ah bossku! ğŸ”¥ğŸ€ğŸ’° Don't worry, sometimes our luck goes up and down. Keep playing patiently, maybe a big win will come in the next round! If there's anything I can help with, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Huat ah bossku! ğŸ”¥ğŸ€ğŸ’° Jangan risau, kadang-kadang nasib kita turun naik. Teruskan bermain dengan sabar, mungkin kemenangan besar akan datang dalam pusingan seterusnya! Jika ada apa-apa yang boleh saya bantu, beritahu saja ya!

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been credited to my account yet?
variations: kredit tk masuk lagi

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya belum dimasukkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your credit has not been credited yet, it may be in process. Please wait between 3 to 10 minutes for the system to credit your account. If there is still no change after 10 minutes, please contact live chat for immediate assistance. You will be able to purchase a number for the 9 PM draw once your account is credited.
detailed.ms: Jika kredit anda belum dimasukkan, mungkin ia sedang dalam proses. Sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk sistem mengkreditkan akaun anda. Jika selepas 10 minit masih tiada perubahan, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Anda akan dapat membeli nombor untuk undian 9 malam setelah akaun anda dikreditkan.

question.text: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: After topping up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds will be credited within 1 to 10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, dana akan dikreditkan dalam masa 1 hingga 10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan dana belum dikreditkan, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
variations: topup
how to top up using ATM

languages.en: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya menggunakan ATM?

detailed.en:
To top up using an ATM, follow these steps:
1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers.
2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu.
3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).
4. Enter the top-up amount (Min RM10).
5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt.
6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat.
7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes.

Make sure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection.
If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top-up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini:
1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank.
2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'.
3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi).
4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10).
5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit.
6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam sembang langsung.
7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit.

Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan.
Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam sembang langsung ya!

question.text: I have a J3 win that hasn't been credited yet. What should I do?
variations: saya ada kena ibox J3 jam8mlm tk masuk lgi bos

languages.en: I have a J3 win that hasn't been credited yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: saya ada kena ibox J3 jam8mlm tk masuk lgi bos

detailed.en: If your J3 win has not been credited yet, please wait around 10 minutes for the system to process it. If it still does not appear, you can contact live chat with your transaction details. Thank you for your patience, and I hope you have a big win!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum masuk, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika masih tidak muncul, anda boleh hubungi live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, boss! Semoga anda dapat kemenangan yang besar!

question.text: I bought 03 J3 but cannot access it for 2D. What should I do?

languages.en: I bought 03 J3 but cannot access it for 2D. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya beli 03 J3 tetapi tidak dapat akses untuk 2D. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: To play J3, you can use the Tesla App. Download the Tesla App from the provided link. In the Tesla App, you can bet on 4D for J2, J3, Perdana & Lucky, and check payments & results for this platform. If you encounter any issues or need assistance, just reply in the live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk bermain J3, anda boleh gunakan Aplikasi Tesla. Muat turun Aplikasi Tesla dari pautan yang disediakan. Dalam Aplikasi Tesla, anda boleh bertaruh 4D pada J2, J3, Perdana & Lucky, dan semak pembayaran & keputusan untuk platform ini. Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas saja dalam live chat.

question.text: I made a fast payment, but it hasn't been credited yet. What should I do?
variations: Why hasn't my fast payment been credited yet?
I did a fast payment, but it's still not showing up.

languages.en: I made a fast payment, but it hasn't been credited yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat pembayaran cepat, tetapi ia masih belum dikreditkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have made a fast payment but it hasn't been credited yet, it usually takes 1-3 minutes to process. If it has been more than 3 minutes and still no credit, please check the transaction in your app. If there is still no record, send the complete FPX transaction receipt via live chat for further verification. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat pembayaran cepat tetapi masih belum dikreditkan, biasanya ia mengambil masa 1-3 minit untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih dari 3 minit dan masih tiada, sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi anda. Jika tiada juga, hantar resit transaksi FPX yang lengkap melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!
