Jika selepas itu masih tiada dalam akaun anda, pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit pembayaran di halaman top-up aplikasi. Jika masih ada masalah, anda boleh hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika anda ada kemenangan 4D, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet anda secara automatik, sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam aplikasi.

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account after a Jaguar bet?
variations: Why hasn't my Jaguar bet winnings been credited?
What is the process for winnings crediting?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account after a Jaguar bet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya selepas pertaruhan Jaguar?

detailed.en: If your Jaguar bet winnings at 9 PM have not been credited, please wait between 10 to 30 minutes for the system to process. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for the crediting. If you are using IBOX, the process may take a little longer. If after that period your winnings are still not credited, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan pertaruhan Jaguar anda pada jam 9 malam belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu antara 10 hingga 30 minit untuk sistem memproses. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 malam dan 10:30 malam untuk pengkreditan. Jika anda menggunakan IBOX, proses mungkin mengambil sedikit masa lebih lama. Jika selepas tempoh itu kemenangan anda masih belum dikreditkan, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if my betting winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
variations: belum mask?
*masuk

languages.en: What should I do if my betting winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan pertaruhan saya belum dimasukkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, your betting winnings will be credited to your wallet automatically within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it has not been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hi boss, kemenangan bet bola akan masuk ke wallet secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Mohon bersabar ya boss, sistem sedang proses. Kalau masih belum masuk selepas 24 jam, boleh roger kami di live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: How long does it take for the winnings from a football bet to be credited to my wallet?

languages.en: How long does it take for the winnings from a football bet to be credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: Berapa lama kemenangan dari pertaruhan bola akan dimasukkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: The winnings from a football bet will be automatically credited to your wallet within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it has not been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan dari pertaruhan bola akan dimasukkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Jika ia belum dimasukkan selepas 24 jam, anda boleh menghubungi kami melalui live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!

question.text: What should I do after winning a 4D lottery?

languages.en: What should I do after winning a 4D lottery?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menang loteri 4D?

detailed.en: Congratulations on your 4D win! It's a great opportunity to manage your finances wisely. Consider investing some of your winnings, saving for future needs, and enjoying a portion responsibly. Remember to consult with a financial advisor for the best strategies.
detailed.ms: Tahniah atas kemenangan 4D anda! Ini adalah peluang yang baik untuk menguruskan kewangan anda dengan bijak. Pertimbangkan untuk melaburkan sebahagian daripada kemenangan anda, menyimpan untuk keperluan masa depan, dan menikmati sebahagian dengan bertanggungjawab. Ingat untuk berunding dengan penasihat kewangan untuk strategi terbaik.

question.text: What should I do if my transaction is pending?
variations: transaction pending
status of pending transaction

languages.en: What should I do if my transaction is pending?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi saya sedang pending?

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times, as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali, kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally selected the wrong bank while uploading my receipt?
variations: What to do if I chose the wrong bank?
How to correct a wrong bank selection during receipt upload?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally selected the wrong bank while uploading my receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya buat jika saya tersalah pilih bank semasa memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If you accidentally selected the wrong bank while uploading your receipt, first wait for the system to reject the upload. After it is rejected, you can upload the receipt again, making sure to select the correct bank this time. Do not upload the same receipt twice before it is rejected to avoid issues in the top-up process.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tersalah pilih bank semasa memuat naik resit, tunggu sistem menolak muat naik tersebut. Selepas ia ditolak, anda boleh memuat naik semula resit, pastikan anda memilih bank yang betul kali ini. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama dua kali sebelum ia ditolak untuk mengelakkan masalah dalam proses top-up.

question.text: How does the 4D winning process work and when will the winnings be credited to my wallet?
variations: What should I do if my 4D winnings haven't appeared yet?
Will I be notified if I win or should I check myself?

languages.en: How does the 4D winning process work and when will the winnings be credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: Bagaimana proses kemenangan 4D berfungsi dan bila kemenangan akan dikreditkan ke dalam wallet saya?

detailed.en: If you win in 4D, the winnings will be automatically credited to your JOKER wallet shortly after the game ends. If you do not see the winnings in your wallet, please check your wallet history. If there is still no record, send us a screenshot and we will assist you promptly.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang dalam 4D, kemenangan akan secara automatik dikreditkan ke dalam wallet JOKER anda selepas permainan berakhir. Jika anda tidak melihat kemenangan dalam wallet anda, sila semak sejarah wallet anda. Jika masih tiada rekod, hantarkan tangkapan skrin kepada kami dan kami akan membantu anda dengan cepat.

detailed.en: If your money has not been credited yet, there may be a slight delay in the payment process. Please check with your bank or wait a little longer. If there is anything else I can assist you with, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika duit belum masuk, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan dalam proses pembayaran. Sila semak semula dengan bank anda atau tunggu sekejap lagi. Jika ada apa-apa yang saya boleh bantu, beritahu saja!

question.text: What should I do if my payment via Fast Payment (FPX) has not been processed after 10 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment via Fast Payment (FPX) has not been processed after 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pembayaran saya melalui Fast Payment (FPX) belum diproses selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: If you have topped up via Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the payment should be completed within 1-10 minutes. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah topup melalui Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, pembayaran akan selesai dalam 1-10 minit. Jika ia belum diproses selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up status shows PENDING?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up status shows PENDING?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status top-up saya menunjukkan PENDING?

detailed.en: If your top-up status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it takes more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status top-up anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Is it normal for deposits to take a long time to process?
variations: Bos duit masuk ambik masa lama ke

detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM15 anda belum dikredit, sila semak semula wallet anda dan lihat resit transaksi yang telah dimuat naik. question.text: What are the steps to top up using an ATM?
variations: topup
how to top up using ATM

languages.en: What are the steps to top up using an ATM?
languages.ms: Apakah langkah-langkah untuk top up menggunakan ATM?

detailed.en:
To top up using an ATM, follow these steps:

1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers.
2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu.
3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).
4. Enter the top-up amount (Minimum RM10).
5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt.
6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat.
7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes.

Make sure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection.
If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini:

1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank.
2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'.
3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi).
4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10).
5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit.
6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat.
7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit.

Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan.
Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat!

question.text: How can I upload a receipt if I'm having trouble with the process?

languages.en: How can I upload a receipt if I'm having trouble with the process?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh meng-upload resit jika saya menghadapi masalah dengan proses tersebut?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues uploading your receipt, you can try the following steps: Restart your phone or close and reopen the app. Switch your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa). Ensure your internet connection is stable before trying again. If the problem persists, you can send the receipt directly to live chat for further assistance. We will help process it for you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk meng-upload resit, boleh cuba langkah-langkah ini: Mulakan semula telefon anda atau tutup dan buka semula aplikasi. Cuba tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi ke data mudah alih atau sebaliknya). Pastikan sambungan internet anda stabil sebelum mencuba lagi. Jika masalah masih berterusan, anda boleh hantarkan resit terus ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu prosesnya untuk anda!

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status transaksi saya masih pending?

detailed.en: If your transaction status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times, as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still pending, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status transaksi anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali, kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih pending, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my betting winnings have not been credited to my wallet after placing a bet?
variations: What happens if my winnings don't show up?
How long does it take for betting winnings to be credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my betting winnings have not been credited to my wallet after placing a bet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan pertaruhan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya selepas membuat pertaruhan?

detailed.en: Hi boss, the winnings from your football bet will be credited to your wallet automatically within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it still hasn't been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, kemenangan dari pertaruhan bola anda akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Jika ia masih belum dikreditkan selepas 24 jam, anda boleh menghubungi kami melalui live chat untuk pengesahan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
variations: top-up belum masuk
top-up tidak diterima

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been credited yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat support for further investigation. We will assist you as soon as possible! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila hantarkan resit transaksi lengkap ke sokongan live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™

question.text: What should I do if my prize winnings are not showing up?
variations: Why is my prize not credited?
What happened to my winnings?

languages.en: What should I do if my prize winnings are not showing up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan hadiah saya tidak muncul?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing delays in receiving your winnings, please specify whether it was from 4D, bola, or another game so I can assist you in checking the status.
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami kelewatan dalam menerima kemenangan anda, sila nyatakan sama ada ia dari 4D, bola, atau permainan lain supaya saya boleh membantu anda menyemak statusnya.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
variations: Top up belum masuk, apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
Saya sudah top up tetapi belum dapat kredit, kenapa?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
languages.ms: Top up belum masuk, apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been credited yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not credited, please send the complete transaction receipt via live chat for further verification. We will assist you as soon as possible! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
variations: Why hasn't my money been credited yet?
What to do if the winnings are not showing in my account?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If the money hasn't been credited after 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your betting receipt. I will check and help resolve this issue as soon as possible. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika duit belum masuk selepas 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit pertaruhan anda. Saya akan semak dan bantu selesaikan masalah ini secepat mungkin. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if I made a mistake in the reference name on my deposit receipt?
variations: I made a mistake in the reference name.
What happens if the reference name is incorrect?

languages.en: What should I do if I made a mistake in the reference name on my deposit receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah nama rujukan pada resit deposit?

detailed.en: If you have made a mistake in the reference name on your deposit receipt, there is no problem. It may slow down the verification process, but your funds are safe. Make sure to check carefully in the future. Good luck with your next transaction!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat kesilapan dalam nama rujukan pada resit deposit, tiada masalah. Ia mungkin akan melambatkan proses semakan, tetapi dana anda selamat. Pastikan untuk semak dengan teliti pada masa akan datang. Semoga berjaya dengan transaksi seterusnya!

question.text: How long does it take for the winnings from a bet to be credited to my wallet?

languages.en: How long does it take for the winnings from a bet to be credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: Berapa lama masa yang diambil untuk kemenangan dari pertaruhan dimasukkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, the winnings from a football bet will be credited to your wallet automatically within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it has not been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai boss, kemenangan pertaruhan bola akan dimasukkan ke dalam dompet secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Mohon bersabar ya boss, sistem sedang proses. Kalau masih belum masuk selepas 24 jam, boleh roger kami di live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal fails at Hong Leong Bank?
variations: Why did my withdrawal fail?
How can I resolve a failed withdrawal?

languages.en: What should I do if my withdrawal fails at Hong Leong Bank?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran saya gagal di Hong Leong Bank?

detailed.en: If your withdrawal fails, it may be due to the bank you are using undergoing maintenance. You can try using another bank for the withdrawal or wait a moment and try again. If the problem persists, please contact support via live chat for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran anda gagal, mungkin bank yang anda gunakan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan. Anda boleh cuba menggunakan bank lain untuk pengeluaran atau tunggu sekejap dan cuba lagi. Jika masalah berterusan, sila hubungi sokongan melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
variations: duit win xmsuk lg bos
J3 kena bos

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If you have won, please be patient as the system is processing your winnings, which will be credited to your wallet automatically. You can check the 'Reports' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. If it has been more than 30 minutes and you still do not see the credit, please contact us again with a screenshot of your receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses kemenangan anda, yang akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Jika lebih dari 30 minit dan anda masih tidak melihat kredit, sila hubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan layar resit dan keputusan anda.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up is delayed?
variations: Why is my top-up taking so long?
How can I check the status of my top-up?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up is delayed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya lambat?

detailed.en: If your top-up is delayed, please let me know whether you used ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). This will help me check for you. For ATM/Transfer, please upload the receipt in the top-up section and wait 1-10 minutes; for FPX, the funds should appear within 1-10 minutes. If there is a longer delay, please send a full screenshot via live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda lambat, sila beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX). Ini akan membantu saya semak untuk anda. Untuk ATM/Transfer, sila muat naik resit dalam bahagian top-up dan tunggu 1-10 minit; untuk FPX, dana sepatutnya muncul dalam 1-10 minit. Jika ada kelewatan lebih lama, sila hantar tangkapan skrin penuh melalui live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do if I haven't received my deposit after uploading the receipt?
variations: lama ke
hilang
hilang apa ?
kamu la

languages.en: What should I do if I haven't received my deposit after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya belum menerima deposit saya selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If you haven't received your deposit after more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your receipt, and I will assist you in investigating the issue immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda masih belum menerima kemasukan selepas lebih dari 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit anda, dan saya akan bantu siasat dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: Why is my deposit still pending after uploading the receipt?
variations: What should I do if my deposit is pending?
How long does it take for a deposit to be processed?

languages.en: Why is my deposit still pending after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Mengapa deposit saya masih pending selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If your deposit status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still pending, you can send a message to live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika status deposit anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih pending, anda boleh menghantar mesej ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What time will the payout for Jaguar J3 be credited?
variations: Jaguar J3 biasa payout pukul berapa

languages.en: What time will the payout for Jaguar J3 be credited?
languages.ms: Jaguar J3 biasa payout pukul berapa

detailed.en: The winnings for Jaguar J3 will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit.
detailed.ms: Kemenangan untuk Jaguar J3 akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara pukul 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut.

question.text: Is there a problem with your app? I have topped up but I can't see the receipt.

languages.en: Is there a problem with your app? I have topped up but I can't see the receipt.
languages.ms: Adakah masalah dengan aplikasi anda? Saya sudah top-up tetapi saya tidak dapat melihat resit.

detailed.en: If you have topped up but the receipt does not appear, you can upload proof of transaction or a screenshot in the top-up section of the app. The process usually takes 3-10 minutes. If there is still no entry after that, please contact live chat with a full screenshot for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top-up tetapi slip tidak keluar, anda boleh muat naik bukti transaksi atau tangkapan skrin di bahagian top-up dalam aplikasi. Proses biasanya mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika selepas itu masih tiada kemasukan, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin penuh untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Saya ingin tahu berapa lama proses pengesahan deposit dan bila dana akan dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya.
variations: Berapa hari masuk bos?
Duit tu loom masuk?
Bukan harini hari ke3 dah ke?

languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu berapa lama proses pengesahan deposit dan bila dana akan dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya.

detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah buat deposit, biasanya bonus akan dikreditkan dalam masa 5-10 minit selepas deposit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu dan masih belum masuk, mungkin ada masalah. Saya sarankan untuk hubungi sokongan pelanggan untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang saya boleh bantu, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: What is the status of my bet request and when can I expect to place my bet?
variations: When can I place my bet?
What is the update on my betting request?

languages.en: What is the status of my bet request and when can I expect to place my bet?
languages.ms: Apakah status permintaan pertaruhan saya dan bila saya boleh menjadikannya?

detailed.en: The receipt for your second bet is the same as the one you just uploaded and is currently being processed. Please wait a moment.
detailed.ms: Resit untuk pertaruhan kedua anda adalah sama dengan resit yang anda baru muat naik dan sedang dalam proses. Sila tunggu sebentar.

question.text: Saya baru periksa di bank dan dana belum masuk ke dalam akaun saya. Bolehkah anda membantu saya untuk menyemak status pengeluaran ini?
variations: Ada withdraw jam 11.37 mlm pd 11.04.2024 to belum ada dlm acc saya.
Bole tlg cek status pengeluaran saya?

languages.en: I just checked the bank and the funds have not yet entered my account. Can you help me check the status of this withdrawal?
languages.ms: Saya baru periksa di bank dan dana belum masuk ke dalam akaun saya. Bolehkah anda membantu saya untuk menyemak status pengeluaran ini?

detailed.en: If your withdrawal of RM3000 has not entered your account after 30 minutes, there may be a slight delay in processing. Please check your transaction records. If it is still in Pending status, please wait a little longer. However, if it has been more than 30 minutes, please send a screenshot of the transaction and I will assist you in checking it immediately! Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran RM3000 anda belum masuk ke dalam akaun selepas 30 minit, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan dalam pemprosesan. Sila semak rekod transaksi anda. Jika masih dalam status Pending, tunggu sekejap lagi. Namun, jika sudah lebih 30 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin transaksi dan saya akan bantu semak dengan segera! Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure the transaction is processed correctly?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure the transaction is processed correctly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai akaun saya untuk memastikan transaksi diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: What should I do if my winnings for J3 have not been credited to my wallet by 9 PM?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings for J3 have not been credited to my wallet by 9 PM?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya untuk J3 belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya pada pukul 9 malam?

detailed.en: The winnings for J3 will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit. If it has not been credited after 30 minutes, please contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Duit kemenangan untuk J3 akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Jika ia masih belum dikreditkan selepas 30 minit, sila hubungi kami semula dengan screenshot resit dan keputusan.

question.text: What should I do if I mistakenly entered the wrong amount for a transaction?
variations: I entered the wrong amount earlier.
How can I correct a wrong transaction amount?

languages.en: What should I do if I mistakenly entered the wrong amount for a transaction?
languages.ms: Apa perlu buat jika saya tersalah masukkan amaun untuk transaksi?

detailed.en: If you entered the wrong amount for a transaction, you can correct it by following these steps: 1. Wait for the system to automatically reject the incorrect receipt. 2. After that, re-upload the same receipt. 3. This time, make sure to enter the correct amount when uploading. If you encounter any other issues, feel free to contact us for assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tersalah letak amaun untuk transaksi, anda boleh betulkan dengan cara berikut: 1. Tunggu sistem reject resit secara automatik. 2. Lepas tu, upload semula resit yang sama. 3. Tapi kali ni, isi amaun yang betul masa upload. Jika ada masalah lain, boleh terus roger kami ya.

question.text: What should I do if my money was deducted but the deposit failed?

languages.en: What should I do if my money was deducted but the deposit failed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika duit saya ditolak tetapi deposit gagal?

detailed.en: I understand, if the money has been deducted from your account but the deposit failed, there may be a technical issue or mistake with the transaction method. Please try to deposit again or send the receipt via live chat for further review. If there's anything else I can assist you with, just let me know! ğŸ˜Š
detailed.ms: Saya faham, jika duit sudah ditolak dari akaun tetapi deposit gagal, mungkin ada masalah teknikal atau kesilapan dengan kaedah transaksi. Sila cuba untuk deposit semula atau hantar resit melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang boleh saya bantu, beritahu saja! ğŸ˜Š

question.text: I am unable to upload a recipe. What should I do?
variations: Cannot upload recipe boss
I can't upload my recipe

languages.en: I am unable to upload a recipe. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya tidak dapat memuat naik resit. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you are unable to upload the recipe and it keeps loading, try these steps: Restart your phone or close and reopen the app. Switch your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa). Ensure your internet connection is stable before trying to upload the recipe again. If the problem persists, you can send the recipe directly to live chat for further assistance. We will help process it for you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda tidak dapat memuat naik resit dan ia terus memuat, cuba langkah-langkah ini: Mulakan semula telefon anda atau tutup & buka semula aplikasi. languages.en: Why can't I withdraw my winnings of RM800 after depositing RM1000 and winning RM1800?

detailed.en: If you have won RM1800 and want to withdraw RM800 but are unable to, there may be withdrawal conditions that need to be met. Typically, if you have wagered 30% of your deposit, you should be able to withdraw your winnings. If you are still facing issues, I recommend contacting customer support for further clarification. They can help check your situation more accurately.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah menang RM1800 dan ingin mengeluarkan RM800 tetapi masih tidak dapat, mungkin ada syarat pengeluaran yang perlu dipenuhi. Biasanya, jika anda sudah mencuci 30% dari deposit, anda sepatutnya boleh mengeluarkan kemenangan. Jika anda masih menghadapi masalah, saya sarankan anda hubungi sokongan pelanggan untuk mendapatkan penjelasan lanjut. Mereka dapat membantu menyemak situasi anda dengan lebih tepat.

question.text: What should I do if I mistakenly credited the wrong amount to my account?
variations: What happens if I transfer the wrong amount?
How can I fix a wrong credit transaction?

languages.en: What should I do if I mistakenly credited the wrong amount to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah kredit jumlah ke akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you mistakenly transferred to your own bank account, unfortunately, the funds cannot be returned. However, you can still use the credited amount for gaming. Make sure to top-up correctly by uploading your bank-in slip through (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). After submission, wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not arrive within 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tersalah transfer ke akaun bank sendiri, sayangnya wang tersebut tidak boleh dipulangkan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan jumlah yang telah dikreditkan untuk permainan. Pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul dengan memuat naik slip bank-in anda melalui (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). Selepas penghantaran, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika kredit tidak tiba dalam masa 10 minit, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if there is no transaction history for my top-up?
variations: Why is there no transaction history for my top-up?
What are the reasons for not seeing my transaction history?

languages.en: What should I do if there is no transaction history for my top-up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika tiada sejarah transaksi untuk top-up saya?

detailed.en: If there is no transaction history for your top-up, there could be several reasons. If you used IBG transfer, the process usually takes 1-3 working days. Make sure to keep the transfer receipt. If after 3 days the funds are still not credited, please contact support via live chat with your transaction details for further assistance. If there was an error in the amount or account used, it is important to report the issue as soon as possible. If you need further assistance, let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika tiada sejarah transaksi untuk top-up anda, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Jika anda menggunakan pemindahan IBG, prosesnya biasanya mengambil masa 1-3 hari bekerja. Pastikan anda menyimpan resit pemindahan. Jika selepas 3 hari dana masih belum dikreditkan, sila hubungi sokongan melalui live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika ada kesilapan dalam jumlah atau akaun yang digunakan, penting untuk melaporkan isu tersebut secepat mungkin. Jika anda perlukan bantuan lebih lanjut, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: How long does it take for a top-up to be processed if it is still pending?

detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda masih dalam status pending, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Anda boleh semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantarkan resit transaksi lengkap ke dalam live chat untuk pemeriksaan segera. Kami akan bantu proses secepat mungkin!

detailed.ms: Terima kasih atas sokongan anda! Jika anda mempunyai lebih banyak soalan, jangan ragu untuk membalas! Semoga anda sentiasa berjaya dan makmur!

question.text: How can I upload my top-up receipt in the app?
variations: What are the steps to upload a receipt?
Can you guide me on uploading a top-up receipt?

languages.en: How can I upload my top-up receipt in the app?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh muat naik resit top-up saya dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: To upload your receipt, please follow these steps: 1. Go to the top-up page in the app. 2. Select the top-up method used (ATM/Transfer or Fast Payment). 3. Choose the bank and enter the amount topped up. 4. Upload a clear and complete image of the transaction receipt. 5. Press 'Submit' and wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to verify. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, you can send the receipt to live chat for immediate checking. If you have any other questions, feel free to contact us in live chat!
detailed.ms: Untuk memuat naik resit anda, sila ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi. 2. Pilih kaedah topup yang digunakan (ATM/Transfer atau Fast Payment). 3. Pilih bank dan masukkan jumlah yang ditopup. 4. Muat naik gambar resit transaksi yang jelas & lengkap. 5. Tekan 'Submit' dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Jika ada pertanyaan lain, boleh roger kami di live chat ya!

question.text: How can I top up my BLM account and what are the minimum amounts required?
variations: top up BLM masuk bos

languages.en: How can I top up my BLM account and what are the minimum amounts required?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun BLM saya dan apakah jumlah minimum yang diperlukan?

detailed.en: To top up your BLM account, the minimum amounts are as follows: For ATM/Transfer, the minimum is RM10, and for Fast Payment (FPX), the minimum is RM50. After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up akaun BLM anda, jumlah minimum adalah seperti berikut: Untuk ATM/Transfer, minimum adalah RM10, dan untuk Pembayaran Pantas (FPX), minimum adalah RM50. Selepas top up, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum dimasukkan selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Is the payment for the 2D J3 at 9 PM usually slow?

languages.en: Is the payment for the 2D J3 at 9 PM usually slow?
languages.ms: Adakah pembayaran untuk 2D J3 pada 9 PM biasanya lambat?

detailed.en: The winnings for J3 are usually credited automatically to your wallet. Please wait a moment as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have a big win!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan untuk J3 biasanya akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila tunggu sebentar, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda dapat kemenangan besar!

question.text: What are the implications of winning in 4D lottery?

languages.en: What are the implications of winning in 4D lottery?
languages.ms: Apakah implikasi menang dalam loteri 4D?

detailed.en: Winning in the 4D lottery can bring significant financial gain, leading to happiness and excitement. However, it is important to manage the winnings wisely and consider the implications of sudden wealth.
detailed.ms: Menang dalam loteri 4D boleh membawa keuntungan kewangan yang besar, yang membawa kepada kebahagiaan dan kegembiraan. Namun, adalah penting untuk menguruskan kemenangan dengan bijak dan mempertimbangkan implikasi kekayaan yang tiba-tiba.

How can I resolve a delayed top-up?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up is delayed after making a deposit?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya lambat selepas membuat deposit?

detailed.en: If your top-up is delayed, please let me know if you are using ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). For ATM/Transfer, ensure you have uploaded the receipt in the top-up section and wait 1-10 minutes. For FPX, the funds should appear within 1-3 minutes. If it is still delayed, please send a full screenshot via live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda lambat, sila beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX). Untuk ATM/Transfer, pastikan anda telah muat naik resit di bahagian top-up dan tunggu 1-10 minit. Untuk FPX, dana sepatutnya muncul dalam 1-3 minit. Jika masih lambat, sila hantar tangkapan layar penuh melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut.

question.text: Bolehkah anda memberitahu saya mengapa duit saya mengambil masa yang lama untuk masuk?
variations: Lama btol duit nak masuk ni
Kenapa duit saya belum masuk?
Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika duit belum masuk?

languages.en: Can you tell me why my money is taking so long to arrive?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda memberitahu saya mengapa duit saya mengambil masa yang lama untuk masuk?

detailed.en: I understand, boss! If the money hasn't arrived after 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of the receipt and I will investigate immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Faham, boss! Jika duit belum masuk selepas 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit dan saya akan siasat dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do if I experience delays in the online demo game?

languages.en: What should I do if I experience delays in the online demo game?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya mengalami kelewatan dalam permainan demo dalam talian?

detailed.en: Unfortunately, there is no option to address delays in the demo mode of the game at this time. However, you can start with small bets using real money, with a minimum of RM10, to experience the game without significant risk. If you need anything else, please let me know.
detailed.ms: Malangnya, tiada pilihan untuk menangani kelewatan dalam mod demo permainan pada masa ini. Namun, anda boleh mula dengan pertaruhan kecil menggunakan wang sebenar, dengan minimum RM10, untuk merasai permainan tanpa risiko besar. Jika anda memerlukan apa-apa lagi, sila beritahu saya.

question.text: What time will I receive points if I win?
variations: When will I get my points for winning?
At what time are points credited after a win?

languages.en: What time will I receive points if I win?
languages.ms: Pukul berapa saya akan menerima mata jika saya menang?

detailed.en: For the Jaguar win at 9 PM, it will usually be credited automatically to your wallet. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for confirmation. If you are using IBOX, the process may take a little longer. If after that period your winnings are still not credited, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Untuk kemenangan bet Jaguar pada pukul 9 malam, ia biasanya akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Report' antara pukul 10:00 malam hingga 10:30 malam untuk pengesahan. Jika anda menggunakan IBOX, proses mungkin mengambil sedikit masa lebih lama. Jika selepas tempoh itu kemenangan anda masih belum dikreditkan, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if my J3 winnings have not been credited yet?
variations: Why hasn't my J3 winnings been credited?
What is the status of my J3 winnings?

languages.en: What should I do if my J3 winnings have not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings are still showing as PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your transaction. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it may slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status has not changed, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda masih menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses transaksi anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia boleh melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status tidak berubah, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my transfer has not been processed and I am experiencing delays with my top-up?
variations: Why is my transfer taking so long?
What can I do if my top-up hasn't gone through?
How long does it take for a top-up to be processed?

languages.en: What should I do if my transfer has not been processed and I am experiencing delays with my top-up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pemindahan saya belum diproses dan saya mengalami kelewatan dengan top-up saya?

detailed.en: If you have transferred money but it has not yet been credited, there may be a delay in the system. Typically, the confirmation process takes 3-10 minutes. If it has been more than that, please check your transaction records. If it is still pending, wait a moment. If it has been more than 30 minutes, send your transaction proof to us via live chat for further verification. I am here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah memindahkan wang tetapi masih belum dikreditkan, mungkin ada kelewatan dalam sistem. Biasanya, proses pengesahan mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu, sila semak rekod transaksi anda. Jika ia masih dalam status Pending, tunggu sebentar. Jika lebih dari 30 minit, hantar bukti transaksi kepada kami melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Saya di sini untuk membantu!

question.text: Bila wang kemenangan Man City akan dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

languages.ms: Bila wang kemenangan Man City akan dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, kemenangan bet bola akan masuk ke wallet secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Mohon bersabar ya boss, sistem sedang proses. Kalau masih belum masuk selepas 24 jam, boleh roger kami di live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!
detailed.ms: Hi boss, kemenangan bet bola akan masuk ke wallet secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Mohon bersabar ya boss, sistem sedang proses. Kalau masih belum masuk selepas 24 jam, boleh roger kami di live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: I haven't received my points yet, what should I do?
variations: Why haven't my points been credited?
What to do if points are not showing up?

languages.en: I haven't received my points yet, what should I do?
languages.ms: Saya belum menerima poin saya, apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If your points have not been credited, you should first try refreshing the app or logging out and logging back in. If the points still do not appear, please contact customer support for further assistance. Additionally, if you are topping up and the points are still not showing, you only need to upload the receipt once and wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to verify. If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will take longer to process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the points still haven't appeared, send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate review.
detailed.ms: Jika poin anda belum dikreditkan, anda harus cuba menyegarkan aplikasi atau log keluar dan log masuk semula. Jika poin masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan pelanggan untuk bantuan lanjut. Selain itu, jika anda melakukan topup dan poin masih tidak muncul, anda hanya perlu memuat naik resit sekali sahaja dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika anda memuat naik resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan menolak transaksi dan ia akan mengambil masa lebih lama untuk diproses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan poin masih belum muncul, hantarkan resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been processed after 12 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been processed after 12 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya tidak diproses selepas 12 minit?

detailed.en: I apologize for the delay! Usually, the top-up process takes 3-10 minutes. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, please send the complete transaction receipt via live chat for further verification. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Saya minta maaf atas kelewatan ini! Biasanya, proses top-up mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum masuk, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: I am experiencing issues with the top-up process in the Joker game. Can you help me understand why my top-up is delayed?
variations: top up sedut top up sedut aiii ntah lah joker
top up tadi mana hare lahhh joker ni
problem problem joker ni skg paling teruk joker dri semua permaiana dn service out
dengan tak bayar dengan. sedut laju aiii joker joker bersabar sya dengan sistem game korang ni
dengan tak bayar dengan sedut laju hare chi yi babi

detailed.en: If your top-up is delayed, it usually takes 3-10 minutes. If it takes longer, the system might be busy. Please wait a moment, and if there are still no updates, send a screenshot of your receipt via live chat for immediate review. Don't worry, we will help resolve this issue!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda lambat, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika lebih dari itu, mungkin sistem sedang sibuk. Sila tunggu sebentar, dan jika masih tiada kemas kini, hantar tangkapan skrin resit anda melalui live chat untuk semakan segera. Jangan risau, kita akan bantu selesaikan masalah ini!

question.text: What should I do if I mistakenly transferred below the minimum top-up amount?
variations: How can I resolve a mistake transfer that is below the minimum top-up?
What steps should I take for a transfer that is less than the required top-up amount?

languages.en: What should I do if I mistakenly transferred below the minimum top-up amount?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah transfer di bawah jumlah top-up minimum?

detailed.en: To top up successfully, please follow these steps: 1ï¸âƒ£ Make an additional transfer to reach the RM10 minimum. 2ï¸âƒ£ Then upload both transaction receipts via live chat (âŒ Do not upload them on the top-up page) so we can combine the total and process your top-up. Once submitted, please wait 3â€“10 minutes for the system to verify. If you have any other questions, just let us know, boss! ğŸ”„ğŸ’°âœ¨
detailed.ms: Untuk menambah jumlah, anda perlu: 1ï¸âƒ£ Lakukan transfer tambahan untuk mencapai RM10. 2ï¸âƒ£ Setelah itu, muat naik kedua-dua resit transaksi ke dalam live chat (âŒ Jangan muat naik ke halaman top-up) supaya kami boleh menggabungkan jumlah tersebut dan memproses top-up anda. Setelah menghantar resit, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika ada sebarang pertanyaan lain, beritahu saja ya, boss! ğŸ”„ğŸ’°âœ¨

question.text: What should I do after winning a jackpot?

languages.en: What should I do after winning a jackpot?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menang jackpot?

detailed.en: Congratulations on your jackpot win! It's a great opportunity to celebrate and consider how to manage your winnings wisely. You might want to consult with a financial advisor to discuss investment options or saving strategies. Enjoy your win and make the most of it!
detailed.ms: Tahniah atas kemenangan jackpot anda! Ini adalah peluang yang baik untuk meraikan dan mempertimbangkan cara untuk menguruskan kemenangan anda dengan bijak. Anda mungkin ingin berunding dengan penasihat kewangan untuk membincangkan pilihan pelaburan atau strategi simpanan. Nikmati kemenangan anda dan manfaatkan sebaiknya!

question.text: Is there any update regarding my 4D winnings?
variations: What is the status of my 4D winnings?
When will my 4D winnings be credited?

languages.en: Is there any update regarding my 4D winnings?
languages.ms: Ada tak sebarang kemas kini mengenai kemenangan 4D saya?

detailed.en: Hello boss ğŸ˜Š If you have won a 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little time today. The winning money will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please check from time to time in the app. If it has not been credited after more than 30 minutes, you can contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Salam boss ğŸ˜Š Kalau ada nombor 4D kena, mohon boss sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet boss secara automatik. Sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam app. Kalau lebih 30 minit masih belum masuk, boleh roger kami semula dengan screenshot resit & result ya boss ğŸ™ğŸ”¥

question.text: What should I do if my transaction is not confirmed after making a deposit?
variations: What to do if my deposit is not confirmed?
How can I resolve an unconfirmed transaction?

languages.en: What should I do if my transaction is not confirmed after making a deposit?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi saya tidak disahkan selepas membuat deposit?

detailed.en: If you have deposited RM33 but have not received confirmation, please wait a moment. If it takes more than 10 minutes, send a screenshot of the receipt and I will assist you in checking it immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah bank in RM33, tetapi belum ada pengesahan, sila tunggu sekejap. Jika ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, hantar tangkapan skrin resit dan saya akan bantu semak dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do if I cannot use Fast Payment (FPX) through Touch 'n Go?

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot use Fast Payment (FPX) through Touch 'n Go?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat menggunakan Pembayaran Pantas (FPX) melalui Touch 'n Go?

detailed.en: Currently, Fast Payment (FPX) through Touch 'n Go is under maintenance. You can try other methods for top-up: ATM/Transfer (DuitNow / Instant Transfer) with a minimum of RM10, or Fast Payment (FPX) through other banks with a minimum of RM50. If you still have issues or need assistance, please contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Sekarang, Pembayaran Pantas (FPX) melalui Touch 'n Go sedang dalam penyelenggaraan. Anda boleh mencuba kaedah lain untuk topup: ATM/Transfer (DuitNow / Instant Transfer) dengan minimum RM10, atau Pembayaran Pantas (FPX) melalui bank lain dengan minimum RM50. Jika anda masih mempunyai masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure my transaction is processed?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup akaun saya untuk memastikan transaksi saya diproses?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Saya mengalami masalah dengan top-up iBox 2081 yang belum dikreditkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up iBox saya belum dikreditkan?
Bagaimana cara menyelesaikan masalah top-up iBox 2081?

languages.en: I am experiencing an issue with my iBox 2081 top-up that has not been credited. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya mengalami masalah dengan top-up iBox 2081 yang belum dikreditkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing an issue with the iBox top-up that has not been credited, the process usually takes 3-10 minutes. If it still does not appear after that, please check your wallet or send a screenshot of the receipt via live chat. If you have any other questions, feel free to ask! Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah dengan top-up iBox yang belum dikreditkan, biasanya prosesnya mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika selepas itu masih belum muncul, sila semak dompet anda atau hantar tangkapan skrin resit melalui live chat. Jika ada pertanyaan lain, jangan ragu untuk bertanya! Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if the link I received is not working?
variations: The link doesn't work, what can I do?
I can't access the link, any suggestions?

languages.en: What should I do if the link I received is not working?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pautan yang saya terima tidak berfungsi?

detailed.en: If the link you received is not functioning, there may be a technical issue. You can try refreshing the page or using a different device. If the problem persists, please let me know, and I will assist you in resolving it!
detailed.ms: Jika pautan yang anda terima tidak berfungsi, mungkin ada masalah teknikal. Anda boleh cuba menyegarkan halaman atau menggunakan peranti lain. Jika masalah berterusan, sila beritahu saya, dan saya akan membantu anda menyelesaikannya!

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally topped up only RM9 instead of the minimum RM10 required for the top-up process?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally topped up only RM9 instead of the minimum RM10 required for the top-up process?
languages.ms: Apa perlu buat jika saya terisi hanya RM9 dan bukannya minimum RM10 yang diperlukan untuk proses topup?

detailed.en: To proceed with the top-up, you need to transfer an additional RM10 to meet the minimum requirement of RM10. Once you do that, the total will be combined to RM19, and we will process your top-up. Please ensure to send the receipts within 24 hours to this live chat, not through the app.
detailed.ms: Untuk meneruskan proses topup, anda perlu memindahkan tambahan RM10 untuk memenuhi syarat minimum RM10. Setelah itu, jumlah akan digabungkan menjadi RM19 dan kami akan memproses topup anda. Sila pastikan untuk menghantar resit dalam tempoh 24 jam ke sini (live chat), bukan melalui aplikasi.

question.text: What should I do if my payment of 2277 has not been credited yet?
variations: What happens if my payment is not credited?
How long should I wait for my payment to be credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment of 2277 has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pembayaran saya sebanyak 2277 belum dikredit?

detailed.en: If you have already made the payment but the funds have not been credited, please wait for about 3-10 minutes. If it still hasn't been credited after that, please contact live chat for immediate assistance. I hope everything will be resolved quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah membuat pembayaran tetapi dana belum dikredit, sila tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit. Jika masih belum dikredit selepas itu, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Saya harap semuanya akan selesai dengan cepat!

question.text: Can you provide information about items that have already been redeemed?

languages.en: Can you provide information about items that have already been redeemed?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda memberikan maklumat tentang barangan yang sudah ditebus?

detailed.en: For items that have already been redeemed, the delivery process usually takes 2-3 weeks. If you need any other information, such as full name, phone number, and address, please provide it so we can process it quickly. If you have any other questions, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Untuk barangan yang sudah ditebus, proses penghantaran biasanya mengambil masa 2-3 minggu. Jika anda memerlukan maklumat lain, seperti nama penuh, nombor telefon, dan alamat, sila berikan supaya kami dapat memprosesnya dengan cepat. Jika ada soalan lain, jangan segan untuk bertanya!

question.text: What should I do if all games cannot be opened?
variations: semua game tidak boleh buka

languages.en: What should I do if all games cannot be opened?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika semua permainan tidak boleh dibuka?

detailed.en: To fix the issue of games not opening, try the following steps: 1. Close and reopen the game application. 2. Log out and log back into the Joker app, then try again. 3. Change your internet connection (try WiFi or mobile data). 4. Check if the game is under maintenance â€“ if so, wait until it is completed. 5. Try reinstalling the game using the correct link. If it still cannot be opened, send a screenshot of the error to live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk memperbaiki masalah permainan yang tidak dibuka, cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi permainan. 2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam aplikasi Joker, kemudian cuba lagi. 3. Tukar sambungan internet (cuba WiFi atau data mudah alih). 4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan â€“ jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai. 5. Cuba pasang semula permainan menggunakan pautan yang betul. Jika masih tidak boleh dibuka, hantar tangkapan layar kesilapan ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: Saya telah mengikuti langkah-langkah yang sama seperti semalam tetapi masih tidak dapat log masuk. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

languages.ms: saya telah mengikuti langkah-langkah yang sama seperti semalam tetapi masih tidak dapat log masuk. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you are still unable to log in, please try the following steps: 1. Ensure your username and password are correct. 2. Clear your browser's cache and cookies. 3. If it still doesn't work, try using a different browser or the mobile app. If the problem persists, let me know and I am here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika anda masih tidak dapat log masuk, boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Pastikan nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda betul. 2. Cuba kosongkan cache dan cookies pelayar anda. 3. Jika masih tidak berjaya, cuba gunakan pelayar lain atau aplikasi mudah alih. Jika masalah berterusan, beritahu saya ya! Saya sedia membantu!

question.text: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: After topping up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds will be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, dana akan dikreditkan dalam masa 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan dana belum dikreditkan, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: What is the status of my winnings from the betting match earlier?

languages.en: What is the status of my winnings from the betting match earlier?
languages.ms: Apakah status kemenangan saya dari perlawanan pertaruhan tadi?

detailed.en: Hi boss, the winnings from the betting match will be automatically credited to your wallet within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it has not been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, kemenangan dari perlawanan pertaruhan akan dimasukkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Jika ia masih belum dimasukkan selepas 24 jam, anda boleh menghubungi kami melalui live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?
variations: What steps do I need to take after topping up?
How can I confirm my top-up transaction?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai untuk memastikan transaksi saya diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt on the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit di halaman tambah nilai dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum diproses selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk pengesahan segera.

question.text: What assistance can I provide you with today, boss?

languages.ms: Apa bantuan yang boleh saya berikan kepada anda hari ini, bos?

detailed.en: I'm here to help you with anything you need. Just let me know!
detailed.ms: Saya di sini untuk membantu anda dengan apa sahaja yang anda perlukan. Beritahu saya sahaja!

question.text: What do I need to upload for my transaction?

languages.en: What do I need to upload for my transaction?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya muat naik untuk transaksi saya?

detailed.en: Please upload a clear image of the receipt that shows the following details: Successful status, Amount, Time/Date, and Recipient.
detailed.ms: Sila muat naik gambar resit yang jelas yang menunjukkan butiran berikut: Status Berjaya, Jumlah, Masa/Tarikh, dan Penerima.

detailed.en: Once you have topped up, make sure to upload the transaction receipt to the top-up page in the app, not in the live chat. After uploading, wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, please reply to us in the live chat for further checks.
detailed.ms: Baik, boss! ğŸ˜Š Jika anda sudah top-up, pastikan resit transaksi telah dimuat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan di live chat. Selepas memuat naik, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum masuk, sila balas kepada kami di live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. ğŸ™ğŸ”¥

question.text: What should I do if my deposit hasn't been credited yet?
variations: kredit BLM masuk
topup belum masuk

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit hasn't been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If your deposit of RM15 hasn't been credited yet, make sure to check your transaction receipt and your wallet. Sometimes, there may be delays due to certain conditions. If you have checked and still see no credit, I recommend contacting customer support via live chat for further assistance. Please be patient as the system will process it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM15 anda belum masuk, pastikan anda telah menyemak resit transaksi dan juga wallet anda. Kadang-kadang, ada kelewatan disebabkan syarat tertentu. Jika anda sudah semak dan masih tiada kemasukan, saya sarankan anda hubungi sokongan pelanggan melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Mohon bersabar ya boss, sistem akan proses secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if my recent transaction has not been processed yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my recent transaction has not been processed yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi terbaru saya belum diproses?

detailed.en: If you have just made a transaction and it has not been processed yet, there may be a slight delay in the process. Typically, it takes between 3 to 10 minutes for confirmation. If there is still no entry, please double-check the receipt and ensure it has been uploaded correctly. If there are any other issues, let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda baru sahaja membuat transaksi dan masih belum diproses, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan dalam proses. Biasanya, ia mengambil masa antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika masih tiada kemasukan, sila semak semula resit dan pastikan ia telah dimuat naik dengan betul. Jika ada masalah lain, beritahu saya!

question.text: Why am I not able to win the jackpot in the game?
variations: Why can't I get the jackpot?
What is the reason for not winning the jackpot?

languages.en: Why am I not able to win the jackpot in the game?
languages.ms: Kenapa saya tidak dapat menang jackpot dalam permainan?

detailed.en: I understand your feelings. Sometimes luck does not favor us. But don't worry, fortune can come at any time! The key is to enjoy the game and try again calmly. I wish you lots of luck and hope you hit the jackpot in the next round!
detailed.ms: Saya faham perasaan anda. Kadang-kadang, nasib tidak menyebelahi kita. Tapi jangan risau, rezeki boleh datang bila-bila masa! Kuncinya adalah untuk menikmati permainan dan cuba lagi dengan tenang. Saya doakan anda banyak luck dan semoga dapat jackpot dalam pusingan seterusnya!

variations: Lambat masok wallet
Masih blm masok lagi bos

languages.en: Why is my wallet not credited yet after winning?
languages.ms: Lambat masok wallet

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your transaction. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times, as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, you can send a screenshot of the receipt to live chat for further investigation.
detailed.ms: Jika status tunjuk PENDING, maksudnya sistem tengah proses sekarang ya. Mohon boss tunggu dulu sampai sistem selesai proses. Jangan upload resit banyak kali, sebab akan buat proses jadi lambat. Kalau lebih 10 minit belum selesai, boleh hantar ke live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

detailed.ms: Jika duit belum masuk selepas anda upload resit, biasanya ia mengambil masa antara 1 hingga 10 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit anda melalui live chat supaya kami boleh semak dengan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

Kalau ada nombor 4D kena, mohon boss sabar ya

You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the winnings have not been credited, please contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
variations: My top-up hasn't arrived yet, what should I do?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been credited yet, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes after uploading the receipt. If the funds still do not appear, please contact live chat support with your complete receipt. Additionally, if you have topped up via Fast Payment (FPX), please wait 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, it should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it takes longer than 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika dana masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda. Selain itu, jika anda telah top-up melalui Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, ia akan dikreditkan dalam 1-10 minit. Jika ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika baki saya RM0 dan saya ingin bermain?

detailed.en: If your balance is RM0 and you want to play, you need to make a minimum deposit of RM10 to start. If you have any issues with the deposit or other questions, please let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika baki anda RM0 dan anda ingin bermain, anda perlu membuat deposit minimum RM10 untuk mula. Jika ada masalah dengan deposit atau pertanyaan lain, beritahu saya, ya!

question.text: I have already withdrawn my funds, can you please proceed with the transaction?

languages.en: I have already withdrawn my funds, can you please proceed with the transaction?
languages.ms: Saya sudah mengeluarkan dana saya, bolehkah anda meneruskan transaksi?

detailed.en: If the withdrawal has not been approved yet, don't worry! It usually takes 5-30 minutes to process. If it has not been credited after 30 minutes, please reply to us in the live chat and send the transaction details for immediate checking. We will help you check it, boss!
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran belum diluluskan, jangan risau! Biasanya, ia mengambil masa 5-30 minit untuk diproses. Jika selepas 30 minit ia masih belum dikreditkan, balas kepada kami dalam chat langsung dan hantarkan butiran transaksi untuk pemeriksaan segera. Kami akan bantu semak untuk anda, boss!

question.text: I have uploaded my receipt but the funds have not been credited yet. Can you help me check this issue?
variations: I have uploaded my receipt but it hasn't gone through.

detailed.en: If you have uploaded your receipt but the funds have not been credited yet, there may be an issue in the system. Please wait a little longer, and if there is still no update, I recommend sending your transaction details via live chat so we can assist you further. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah muat naik resit tetapi wang masih belum dimasukkan, mungkin ada masalah dalam sistem. Sila tunggu sekejap lagi, dan jika masih tiada, saya sarankan anda hantar maklumat transaksi melalui live chat supaya kami dapat bantu semak dengan lebih lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!
