question.text: Can you check the status of my withdrawal request for RM30 and RM70?
variations: whitdraw rm30 tolong check
whitdraw rm70 bos tolong check

languages.ms: whitdraw rm30 tolong check

detailed.en: For a withdrawal of RM30, it usually takes 5-30 minutes to process. If it has not been received after 30 minutes, please provide the transaction details and we will check for you. For a withdrawal of RM70, ensure you meet the minimum withdrawal requirement of RM10 and have won at least 30% of your capital. If all conditions are met, the withdrawal will also be processed within 5-30 minutes. If there are any issues or further questions, let me know!
detailed.ms: Untuk pengeluaran RM30, biasanya ia akan diproses dalam masa 5-30 minit. Jika ia masih belum diterima selepas 30 minit, sila berikan butiran transaksi dan kami akan semak untuk anda. Untuk pengeluaran RM70, pastikan anda telah memenuhi syarat minimum pengeluaran iaitu RM10 dan telah menang sekurang-kurangnya 30% daripada modal anda. Jika semua syarat dipenuhi, pengeluaran akan diproses dalam masa 5-30 minit. Jika ada masalah atau pertanyaan lain, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: I have a balance of 0.50, but it is not enough. What should I do to top up my account?
variations: How can I top up my account if my balance is low?
What is the minimum amount to top up using Touch 'n Go?

languages.en: I have a balance of 0.50, but it is not enough. What should I do to top up my account?
languages.ms: Saya mempunyai baki 0.50, tetapi ia tidak mencukupi. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk menambah baki saya?

detailed.en:
To top up using Touch 'n Go (TNG), the minimum amount is RM10. If you deposited RM15 but it hasn't reflected, there might be a specific issue. Please ensure you follow these steps:

1. Open the TNG eWallet app and go to the 'Transfer' section.
2. Select DuitNow Transfer.
3. Enter the company account number (refer to the top-up page).
4. Enter the correct amount and confirm the transaction.
5. Take a screenshot of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app.

If there are any other issues, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG), jumlah minimum adalah RM10. Jika anda deposit RM15 tetapi tidak masuk, mungkin ada masalah tertentu. Sila pastikan anda mengikuti langkah-langkah ini:

1. Buka aplikasi TNG eWallet dan pergi ke bahagian 'Transfer'.
2. Pilih DuitNow Transfer.
3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat (rujuk halaman top-up).
4. Masukkan jumlah yang betul dan sahkan transaksi.
5. Ambil tangkapan skrin resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.

Jika ada masalah lain, jangan ragu untuk bertanya!

Why is my top-up taking so long?

languages.en: Why is there a long wait for my deposit to be credited?
languages.ms: Kenapa lma sangat tunggu masuk

detailed.en: If your deposit has not been credited, you only need to upload the receipt once and wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to verify it. If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will take longer to process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, please send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate checking. Please be patient, the system will process it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Kalau topup belum masuk, hanya perlu upload resit sekali sahaja dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan ya. ğŸ˜Š Kalau upload resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan reject transaksi & perlu proses semula, jadi lebih lambat. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, baru hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Mohon bersabar ya boss, sistem akan proses secepat mungkin! ğŸ™ğŸ”¥

question.text: Can you provide the download link for the game?
variations: Send link game

languages.en: Can you provide the download link for the game?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda memberikan pautan muat turun untuk permainan?

detailed.en: To download 4D JOKER, please use this link: [https://4djokers.club/chat/download/joker](https://4djokers.club/chat/download/joker). If you encounter any issues during installation, let me know here! Good luck and may you have many wins!
detailed.ms: Untuk muat turun 4D JOKER, sila gunakan pautan ini: [https://4djokers.club/chat/download/joker](https://4djokers.club/chat/download/joker). Jika ada apa-apa masalah semasa pemasangan, beritahu saya terus di sini! Semoga berjaya dan dapat banyak kemenangan!

en: What type of game do you need the link for?
ms: Untuk jenis permainan apa anda memerlukan pautan tersebut?

question.text: Why hasn't my RM20 top-up been credited yet?
variations: in 20
tpi xmsk ag

languages.en: Why hasn't my RM20 top-up been credited yet?
languages.ms: Mengapa top-up RM20 saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your RM20 top-up has been approved, it usually arrives within 5-30 minutes. There may be delays from the bank if it is late. Check your bank recordsâ€”if it is still not there, send a screenshot of the transaction, and I will help resolve it quickly! Thank you for your patience! If you are using Touch 'n Go (TNG) and it hasn't arrived yet, there could be several reasons. If you used Fast Payment (FPX), it typically arrives within 1-3 minutes. If it has been longer than that, check the transaction in your TNG app. If it is still not there, send us the FPX transaction receipt via live chat for further investigation. If you used ATM/Transfer (DuitNow), ensure you have uploaded the transaction receipt on the top-up page and wait 3-10 minutes. If there are any other issues, feel free to contact us!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up RM20 anda sudah diluluskan, biasanya ia akan sampai dalam 5-30 minit. Mungkin ada kelewatan dari pihak bank jika ia lambat. Semak rekod bank andaâ€”jika masih tiada, hantarkan tangkapan skrin transaksi, saya akan bantu selesaikannya dengan cepat! Terima kasih kerana bersabar! Jika anda menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) dan masih belum masuk, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Jika anda menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), biasanya ia akan masuk dalam 1-3 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu, semak transaksi dalam aplikasi TNG anda. Jika masih tiada, hantarkan resit transaksi FPX kepada kami melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Jika anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow), pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit transaksi di halaman top-up dan tunggu 3-10 minit. Kalau ada masalah lain, jangan ragu untuk hubungi kami ya!

question.text: What should I do if my 4D winnings have not been credited to my account?
variations: What happens if my winnings are not credited?
How long does it take for 4D winnings to be credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my 4D winnings have not been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan 4D saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your 4D number wins, the system will automatically credit the winnings to your wallet shortly. To check the 4D results, open the JOKER App, tap the 4D icon, select the Results menu, and compare the numbers and houses with your receipt. If there are any issues or delays, you can send your receipt and result to us for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika nombor 4D anda menang, sistem akan secara automatik memasukkan kemenangan ke dalam dompet anda dalam masa yang singkat. Untuk menyemak keputusan 4D, buka Aplikasi JOKER, tekan ikon 4D, pilih menu Keputusan, dan bandingkan nombor dan rumah dengan resit anda. Jika ada sebarang masalah atau kelewatan, anda boleh menghantar resit dan keputusan kepada kami untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do if I transferred credit to the wrong ID and haven't received my money back?
variations: What can I do if my credit transfer to a friend went wrong?
How can I recover my funds after sending them to the wrong account?

languages.en: What should I do if I transferred credit to the wrong ID and haven't received my money back?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah memindahkan kredit kepada ID yang salah dan belum menerima wang saya kembali?

detailed.en: If you have transferred credit to the wrong ID, I apologize, but the system cannot automatically return it. Please provide me with the wrong JOKER ID you transferred to and the amount of credit involved. We will try to contact the owner of that ID and ask them to return the credit in the same way (Credit Share). However, there is no guarantee that the credit can be returned; it depends on the owner of the ID that received it. For future transfers, please ensure that the ID entered is correct before pressing send.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah transfer kredit kepada ID yang salah, minta maaf ya, sistem tidak boleh mengembalikan secara automatik. Sila berikan saya JOKER ID yang anda transfer secara salah dan jumlah kredit yang terlibat. Kami akan cuba hubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan minta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Credit Share). Namun, tiada jaminan kredit boleh dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerima. Untuk masa akan datang, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum tekan hantar ya!

question.text: What should I do if I have uploaded the same receipt again?

languages.en: What should I do if I have uploaded the same receipt again?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah memuat naik resit yang sama lagi?

detailed.en: Please do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Sila jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: I have topped up RM 100, but it hasn't been credited to my account yet. What should I do?

languages.en: I have topped up RM 100, but it hasn't been credited to my account yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah top-up RM 100, tetapi ia belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If your RM 100 top-up has not been credited, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes for the system to process it. If after that it is still not credited, please send a screenshot of your receipt and I will help resolve this issue. Additionally, if you have made a withdrawal, check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and it is still not credited, send your transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. We will assist you!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up RM 100 anda belum masuk, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika selepas itu masih tiada, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit anda dan saya akan bantu selesaikan masalah ini. Selain itu, jika anda telah membuat pengeluaran, semak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Kami akan bantu semak untuk anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai akaun saya dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit ke halaman tambah nilai dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum masuk selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: How can I top up my account and what should I do if the status shows PENDING?
variations: boss pls top up
user baru

languages.en: How can I top up my account and what should I do if the status shows PENDING?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh menambah nilai akaun saya dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status menunjukkan PENDING?

detailed.en: If your top-up status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still pending, you can send a message to live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status top-up anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghantar mesej ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after submitting my deposit slip for top-up?
variations: How long does it take for the deposit to be approved?
What if my top-up doesn't reflect after submission?

languages.en: What should I do after submitting my deposit slip for top-up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menghantar slip deposit untuk topup?

detailed.en: After you upload the deposit slip, it usually gets approved within 3-5 minutes. Check the 'Transaction Records' page in the app to see if it has been completed. If there are any issues, feel free to let me know! If it takes more than 10 minutes for the transaction to reflect, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas anda muat naik slip deposit, biasanya ia akan diluluskan dalam masa 3-5 minit. Semak halaman 'Rekod Transaksi' dalam aplikasi untuk melihat jika ia sudah selesai. Jika ada masalah, jangan ragu untuk beritahu saya! Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Why hasn't my top-up been credited after 6 minutes?

languages.en: Why hasn't my top-up been credited after 6 minutes?
languages.ms: Mengapa top-up saya belum dikreditkan selepas 6 minit?

detailed.en: If you have already topped up, make sure to upload the transaction receipt to the top-up page in the app. Usually, the verification process takes 3-10 minutes. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, please send the transaction receipt via live chat, and we will check it for you immediately! Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top-up, pastikan resit transaksi diupload ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Biasanya, proses pengesahan mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar resit transaksi melalui live chat, dan kami akan semak dengan segera untuk anda! Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after uploading a new receipt for processing?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading a new receipt for processing?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit baru untuk pemprosesan?

detailed.en: After uploading the receipt, please wait for about 3-10 minutes for the system to process it. If the funds have not been credited after that, please send the receipt via live chat for immediate checking. If you have any other questions, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Selepas memuat naik resit, sila tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika dana masih belum dikreditkan selepas itu, sila hantar resit melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan segera. Jika ada soalan lain, jangan ragu untuk bertanya!

question.text: Why hasn't the money entered my e-wallet yet, even though it's already 10:40?

languages.en: Why hasn't the money entered my e-wallet yet, even though it's already 10:40?
languages.ms: Kenapa duit belum masuk ke e-wallet saya, walaupun sudah pukul 10:40?

detailed.en: If it has been more than 10 minutes and the money has still not entered, please send a screenshot of the receipt and I will investigate immediately. Thank you! Additionally, if you have a winning 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winning money will automatically enter your wallet, so please check from time to time in the app.
detailed.ms: Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan duit masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit dan saya akan siasat dengan segera. Terima kasih! Selain itu, jika anda ada nombor 4D yang menang, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet boss secara automatik, sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam app.

question.text: What transactions have not been processed yet, such as top-up, withdrawal, or game credit?

languages.en: What transactions have not been processed yet, such as top-up, withdrawal, or game credit?
languages.ms: Transaksi apa yang belum diproses, seperti top-up, pengeluaran, atau kredit permainan?

detailed.en: Hi boss, yang belum masuk ni topup, withdraw, atau kredit game? Supaya saya boleh bantu semak untuk boss. ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™
detailed.ms: Hai bos, yang belum masuk ni topup, withdraw, atau kredit game? Supaya saya boleh bantu semak untuk bos. ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™

question.text: Can you please check the status of my top-up?
variations: Top sya tolong check

languages.en: Can you please check the status of my top-up?
languages.ms: Top sya tolong check

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited yet, please wait 3-10 minutes after uploading the receipt. If it still hasn't appeared, please contact support via live chat with the complete receipt. If there is an error in the amount or account, make sure to report it immediately. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, sila tunggu 3-10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika masih tiada, sila hubungi sokongan melalui live chat dengan resit lengkap. Jika ada kesilapan dalam jumlah atau akaun, pastikan untuk melaporkannya segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do when I'm feeling unlucky in a game?

languages.en: What should I do when I'm feeling unlucky in a game?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan apabila saya merasa tidak bernasib baik dalam permainan?

detailed.en: I understand your feelings. If today hasn't brought you luck, remember that tomorrow is still a chance! Keep enjoying the game, as luck can come at any time. I wish you a lot of luck and big wins in the next draw!
detailed.ms: Saya faham perasaan anda. Jika hari ini belum membawa rezeki, ingat bahawa esok masih ada peluang! Teruskan menikmati permainan, kerana nasib boleh datang bila-bila masa. Saya doakan anda banyak rezeki dan kemenangan besar dalam cabutan seterusnya!

question.text: Kawan saya ingin membuka ID baru tetapi tidak dapat masuk kerana sudah mendaftar. Apa yang perlu dilakukan?
variations: Mcm mn nk forgot password
Tlng reset id dia

languages.ms: Kawan saya ingin membuka ID baru tetapi tidak dapat masuk kerana sudah mendaftar. Apa yang perlu dilakukan?

detailed.en: If your friend is having trouble logging in because they have already registered, they can try the following steps: 1. Ensure they are using the correct ID and password. 2. If they forgot their password, they can try to reset it through the 'Forgot Password' option. 3. If the problem persists, they may need to contact customer support via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika kawan anda menghadapi masalah untuk log masuk kerana sudah mendaftar, mungkin dia boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Pastikan dia menggunakan ID dan kata laluan yang betul. 2. Jika dia lupa kata laluan, boleh cuba untuk reset kata laluan melalui pilihan 'Lupa Kata Laluan'. 3. Jika masalah masih berterusan, mungkin dia perlu menghubungi sokongan pelanggan melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: I received a receipt that does not belong to our company. Did I upload the wrong receipt?

languages.en: I received a receipt that does not belong to our company. Did I upload the wrong receipt?
languages.ms: Saya menerima resit yang tidak milik syarikat kami. Adakah saya salah memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: It seems that the receipt you uploaded does not belong to our company. Please check again to ensure you have uploaded the correct receipt.
detailed.ms: Nampaknya resit yang anda muat naik tidak milik syarikat kami. Sila semak semula untuk memastikan anda telah memuat naik resit yang betul.

question.text: I made a mistake in my submission and need to correct the amount I entered.
variations: I submitted the wrong amount.
How do I correct my submission?

languages.en: I made a mistake in my submission and need to correct the amount I entered.
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat kesilapan dalam penghantaran saya dan perlu membetulkan jumlah yang saya masukkan.

detailed.en: You need to submit the correct amount of RM10 instead of RM104. Please resubmit your form with the correct amount.
detailed.ms: Anda perlu menghantar jumlah yang betul iaitu RM10 dan bukannya RM104. Sila hantar semula borang anda dengan jumlah yang betul.

question.text: What should I do if my deposit is still pending after more than 10 minutes?
variations: What to do if my deposit hasn't gone through?
How long does it take for a deposit to process?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit is still pending after more than 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit saya masih dalam status PENDING selepas lebih 10 minit?

detailed.en: If your deposit status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate checking. We will assist you as soon as possible.
detailed.ms: Jika status deposit anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan segera. Kami akan membantu anda secepat mungkin.

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: After successfully uploading the receipt, please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Selepas berjaya memuat naik resit, sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: How can I access my game logs in the application?
variations: kasi buka log game

languages.en: How can I access my game logs in the application?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh mengakses log permainan saya dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: To access your game logs, you can go to the game history section in the application. There, you should be able to see all the games that have been played. If you have any trouble finding it, let me know, and I will assist you further!
detailed.ms: Untuk membuka log permainan, anda boleh pergi ke bahagian sejarah permainan dalam aplikasi. Di situ, anda sepatutnya dapat melihat semua permainan yang telah dimainkan. Jika ada masalah untuk mencarinya, beritahu saya, dan saya akan bantu lebih lanjut!

question.text: What should I do if I cannot open the 918Kiss application?

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot open the 918Kiss application?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat membuka aplikasi 918Kiss?

detailed.en:
To fix the issue of not being able to open 918Kiss, try the following steps:
1. Close and reopen the 918Kiss application.
2. Log out and log back into the Joker App, then re-enter your ID and Password.
3. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa).
4. Check if the game is under maintenance â€“ if so, wait until it is completed.
5. Try reinstalling the game using the correct download links:
   - Download 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com
   - http://b1.918kiss.com
If the problem persists, please respond to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms:
Untuk memperbaiki masalah tidak dapat membuka 918Kiss, cuba langkah-langkah berikut:
1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi 918Kiss.
2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam Aplikasi Joker, kemudian salin semula ID dan Kata Laluan.
3. Cuba tukar sambungan internet (WiFi ke data atau sebaliknya).
4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan â€“ jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai.
5. Cuba pasang semula permainan menggunakan pautan yang betul ini:
   - Muat Turun 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com
   - http://b1.918kiss.com
Jika masalah berterusan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Can you please pray for me as I am feeling unlucky lately?

languages.en: Can you please pray for me as I am feeling unlucky lately?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda doakan saya kerana saya merasa tidak bernasib baik kebelakangan ini?

detailed.en: I understand how you feel. Sometimes luck does not favor us. Don't worry, fortune can come at any time! The key is to enjoy the game and try again calmly. I wish you lots of luck and success in the next round! If you win big, you can make a large withdrawal!
detailed.ms: Saya faham perasaan anda. Kadang-kadang nasib tidak menyebelahi kita. Jangan risau, rezeki boleh datang bila-bila masa! Kuncinya adalah untuk menikmati permainan dan cuba lagi dengan tenang. Saya doakan anda banyak tuah dan semoga berjaya dalam pusingan seterusnya! Jika anda menang besar, anda boleh buat pengeluaran yang banyak!

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: After successfully uploading the receipt, please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Selepas berjaya memuat naik resit, sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin akan melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: How can I change my phone while still using my old ID?
variations: macam mana yaaa

languages.en: How can I change my phone while still using my old ID?
languages.ms: macam mana yaaa

detailed.en: To change your phone and still use your old ID, you just need to log in to the app with the same ID on the new phone. If you encounter any issues during this process, please let me know, and I am here to help!
detailed.ms: Untuk tukar telefon dan masih guna ID lama, anda hanya perlu log masuk ke aplikasi dengan ID yang sama di telefon baru. Jika ada masalah semasa proses tu, beritahu saya, saya sedia membantu!

question.text: What should I do if I am experiencing slow payment or top-up issues?
variations: Knp lme

languages.en: What should I do if I am experiencing slow payment or top-up issues?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya mengalami masalah pembayaran atau top-up yang lambat?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues with slow payments or top-ups, please provide more information so I can assist you better.
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah dengan pembayaran atau top-up yang lambat, sila berikan lebih banyak maklumat supaya saya dapat membantu anda dengan lebih baik.

question.text: How can I play Perdana using the Tesla app?
variations: What do I need to do to play Perdana?
Can you guide me on using the Tesla app for Perdana?

languages.en: How can I play Perdana using the Tesla app?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh bermain Perdana menggunakan aplikasi Tesla?

detailed.en: To play Perdana, you can use the Tesla app. Download the app from the provided link. In the Tesla app, you can bet on 4D for J2, J3, Perdana, and Lucky. You can also check payments and results for this platform. If you have any issues or need assistance, feel free to reply to us in the live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk bermain Perdana, anda boleh menggunakan aplikasi Tesla. Muat turun aplikasi dari pautan yang disediakan. Dalam aplikasi Tesla, anda boleh bertaruh 4D untuk J2, J3, Perdana, dan Lucky. Anda juga boleh menyemak pembayaran dan keputusan untuk platform ini. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila balas kepada kami dalam chat langsung.

question.text: I have topped up RM15, but the RM5 from yesterday has not been credited yet. What should I do?

languages.en: I have topped up RM15, but the RM5 from yesterday has not been credited yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah menambah RM15, tetapi RM5 dari semalam belum dikreditkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If your RM15 deposit has not been credited to your wallet, there may be several reasons. Please check the transaction receipt that you uploaded. Sometimes, deposits may experience delays due to certain terms or conditions. If you have checked and still have issues, please contact our customer support for further assistance. Don't worry, we are here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM15 anda belum dikredit ke wallet, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Sila semak semula resit transaksi yang telah dimuat naik. Kadang-kadang, deposit mungkin mengalami kelewatan disebabkan terma atau syarat tertentu. Jika anda sudah semak dan masih ada masalah, sila hubungi sokongan pelanggan kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Jangan risau, kami sedia membantu!

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. ğŸ˜Š Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit ke halaman tambah nilai dalam aplikasi. ğŸ˜Š Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk pengesahan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been received after waiting for a while?
variations: Kredit tidak masuk
Sudah 10 minit
Masih pending
Kuat makan cibet
Kasi tolong laaaaa.... Aiyoooo

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been received after waiting for a while?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya belum diterima selepas menunggu seketika?

detailed.en: If your credit has not been received after waiting for 10 minutes, please check your transaction records in the app. If it still hasn't been credited, send a screenshot of the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate assistance. We will help you as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika kredit anda belum diterima selepas menunggu 10 minit, sila semak rekod transaksi dalam aplikasi. Jika masih belum dikredit, hantar tangkapan layar resit transaksi kepada live chat untuk kami semak dengan segera. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if my child is sick and I am worried about our financial situation?

languages.en: What should I do if my child is sick and I am worried about our financial situation?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika anak saya sakit dan saya bimbang tentang keadaan kewangan kami?

detailed.en: It's great to hear that you had a win with 4D! I hope this brings you some relief during this tough time. Remember to take care of your health and your child's health as well.
detailed.ms: Bagus mendengar bahawa anda menang 4D! Saya harap ini memberi anda sedikit kelegaan semasa waktu sukar ini. Ingat untuk menjaga kesihatan anda dan kesihatan anak anda juga.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up using Fast Payment is delayed?
variations: Why is my top-up taking so long?
What to do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up using Fast Payment is delayed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya menggunakan Fast Payment lambat?

detailed.en: If you have used Fast Payment and your top-up is still delayed, please wait for 10 minutes as the system processes the transaction. Typically, it should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the amount is still not credited, please send a screenshot of the transaction through live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menggunakan Fast Payment dan top-up anda masih lambat, sila tunggu 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses transaksi. Biasanya, ia sepatutnya dikreditkan dalam 1-10 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan jumlah masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantarkan tangkapan skrin transaksi melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal hasn't been processed yet?
variations: How can I check the status of my withdrawal?
What steps should I take if my withdrawal is delayed?

languages.en: What should I do if my withdrawal hasn't been processed yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran saya belum diproses?

detailed.en: Hi boss, once you have made a withdrawal, you can check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and it still hasn't arrived, you can send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it still hasn't arrived, send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. We will help check for you!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, setelah anda membuat pengeluaran, anda boleh menyemak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan masih belum masuk, anda boleh menghantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Juga, semak dalam wallet untuk melihat jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum masuk, hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Kami akan bantu semak untuk anda!

question.text: Why hasn't my top-up or J3 winnings been credited yet?
variations: Knp blm masuk
Why is my top-up not showing?

languages.en: Why hasn't my top-up or J3 winnings been credited yet?
languages.ms: Knp blm masuk

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings or top-up has not been credited, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. If it has been more than that and it still hasn't appeared, please send a screenshot of your receipt, and I will help resolve this issue promptly. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 atau top-up anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih dari itu dan masih belum muncul, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit anda, dan saya akan bantu selesaikan masalah ini dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa maksudnya apabila status menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?

detailed.en: When the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Apabila status menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit berulang kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: I have made a withdrawal of RM40 but it has not been credited to my account yet. What should I do?

languages.en: I have made a withdrawal of RM40 but it has not been credited to my account yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat pengeluaran RM40 tetapi ia belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: Hi boss, if you have made a withdrawal, please check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, please send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it still hasn't been credited, send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. We will assist you!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, jika anda telah membuat pengeluaran, sila semak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantarkan butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Juga, semak dalam wallet jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum masuk, hantarkan butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Kami akan bantu semak untuk anda!

question.text: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure it is processed correctly?

languages.en: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure it is processed correctly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya sertakan semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian untuk memastikan ia diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: When making an online transfer, please ensure to fill in your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field along with other payment details. This is crucial for us to verify the receipt quickly.
detailed.ms: Semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian, sila pastikan untuk mengisi ID JOKER anda dalam ruangan 'Rujukan Penerima' bersama dengan butiran pembayaran lain. Ini sangat penting untuk kami mengesahkan resit dengan cepat.

question.text: I have made a deposit but the funds have not appeared in my account. What should I do?
variations: Why hasn't my deposit shown up?
What to do if my funds are not credited?
I deposited money but it hasn't been credited yet.

languages.en: I have made a deposit but the funds have not appeared in my account. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat deposit tetapi dana belum muncul dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have made a deposit but the funds have not appeared in your account, please check if you have uploaded the receipt in the top-up section. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds are still not credited, please send us a screenshot of the receipt through live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat deposit tetapi dana belum muncul dalam akaun anda, sila semak sama ada anda telah memuat naik resit di bahagian top-up. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan dana masih tiada kemasukan, sila hantarkan tangkapan skrin resit kepada kami melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Can I get a refund if I deposited money into an account that does not match the registered name?

languages.en: Can I get a refund if I deposited money into an account that does not match the registered name?

detailed.en: Due to company policy, we do not accept deposits with names that differ from the registered name (MUHAMMAD NUR IZZAT BIN AZMAN). Please provide the account number for the name (SITI NORSYAHIRAH BI), and we will process a refund to the owner of that account.

question.text: What should I do if my winnings from the 4D lottery have not been credited to my wallet yet?
variations: Why is my 4D winning not credited?
How long does it take for 4D winnings to appear in my wallet?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings from the 4D lottery have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan 4D saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If you have won in the 4D lottery, please be patient as the system is processing your winnings, which may take some time today. The winnings will be credited to your wallet automatically. You can check the 'Reports' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the winnings have not appeared, please contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang dalam loteri 4D, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses kemenangan anda, yang mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Kemenangan akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Jika lebih dari 30 minit dan kemenangan belum muncul, sila hubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan layar resit dan keputusan.

question.text: How do I top up my account using the app?

languages.en: How do I top up my account using the app?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh menambah nilai akaun saya menggunakan aplikasi?

detailed.en: To top up your account, please take a screenshot of our conversation and upload it in the top-up section of the app as a receipt. Make sure to enter the amount of RM 50 during the upload. After submitting, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to process your top-up. If you have any issues, feel free to contact us via live chat!
detailed.ms: Untuk menambah nilai akaun anda, sila ambil tangkapan skrin perbualan kita dan muat naiknya di bahagian tambah nilai dalam aplikasi sebagai resit. Pastikan untuk mengisi nilai RM 50 semasa muat naik. Selepas menghantar, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem memproses tambah nilai anda. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang masalah, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami melalui sembang langsung!

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk bergabung dengan permainan 4D biasa?
variations: mcm hendak gabung dengan 4D biasa

languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk bergabung dengan permainan 4D biasa?

question.text: What should I do if my status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What should I do if my status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status saya menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?

detailed.en: If your status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: After successfully uploading the receipt, please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Selepas berjaya memuat naik resit, sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: User is looking to deposit RM20 and hopes for a big win during the festive season.
variations: User wants to try their luck with a RM20 deposit.
User is hoping for a big win this festive season.

languages.en: User is looking to deposit RM20 and hopes for a big win during the festive season.
languages.ms: Pengguna ingin mendeposit RM20 dan berharap untuk menang besar semasa musim perayaan.

detailed.en: Deposit RM20 has been received. Wishing you a big win this time! If you need any assistance, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Deposit RM20 sudah diterima. Semoga kali ini dapat ong yang besar! Jika ada apa-apa yang perlu dibantu, beritahu saja ya!

question.text: What should I do if I am having trouble logging in?
variations: How can I resolve login issues?
What steps can I take if I can't log in?

languages.en: What should I do if I am having trouble logging in?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah untuk masuk?

detailed.en: If you are having trouble logging in, please ensure that your username and password are correct, or check your internet connection. If the problem persists, let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda menghadapi masalah untuk masuk, sila pastikan nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda betul, atau semak sambungan internet anda. Jika masalah berterusan, beritahu saya!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up of RM100 has not been processed?
variations: What to do if top-up is not successful?
How to resolve top-up issues?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up of RM100 has not been processed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up RM100 saya tidak diproses?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing difficulties with the top-up, make sure you have followed all the correct steps and uploaded the transaction receipt in the top-up section of the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for confirmation. If it still does not appear after 10 minutes, please send a clear screenshot via live chat for immediate assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami kesukaran untuk top-up, pastikan anda telah mengikuti semua langkah yang betul dan mengupload resit transaksi di bahagian top-up dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika masih tidak muncul selepas 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin yang jelas melalui live chat untuk bantuan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount during a top-up transaction?
variations: How can I correct a wrong top-up amount?
What steps do I need to take for a top-up error?

languages.en: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount during a top-up transaction?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya memasukkan amaun yang salah semasa transaksi top-up?

detailed.en: If you have entered the wrong amount in your top-up, please resend the transaction by uploading the correct receipt with the accurate amount. The system will process the updated top-up within 3-10 minutes. If the credit still does not appear, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your receipt for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memasukkan amaun yang salah dalam top-up, sila hantar semula transaksi dengan memuat naik resit yang betul dengan amaun yang tepat. Sistem akan memproses top-up yang dikemas kini dalam masa 3-10 minit. Jika kredit masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin resit anda untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if my funds have not been credited to my account after making a bank transfer?
variations: Why hasn't my money entered yet?
What to do if the funds are still not in my account?

languages.en: What should I do if my funds have not been credited to my account after making a bank transfer?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika dana saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun selepas membuat pemindahan bank?

detailed.en: If the funds have not been credited to your account even after making a bank transfer, there may be a technical issue or an error with the receipt. Please wait around 3-10 minutes for the system to credit your account. If after 10 minutes it is still not credited, you can contact live chat for immediate assistance. Don't worry, you will be able to purchase numbers for the 9 PM draw once your account is credited.
detailed.ms: Jika dana belum masuk walaupun sudah bank in, mungkin ada masalah teknikal atau kesilapan dengan resit. Sila tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengkreditkan akaun anda. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Jangan risau, anda akan dapat membeli nombor untuk undian 9 malam setelah akaun anda dikreditkan.

languages.en: How to log in to JOKER if the TAC number is not received?

detailed.en: If your friend is not receiving the TAC number to log in to JOKER, there are several steps that can be tried: 1. Check Phone Number: Ensure that the registered phone number is correct and active. 2. Try Again: Ask your friend to resend the TAC request. 3. Check Signal: Make sure the phone has a good signal to receive messages. 4. Contact Support: If still not receiving TAC, it is better to contact customer support for further assistance.

Semak Signal: Pastikan telefon mempunyai signal yang baik untuk menerima mesej. 4. Hubungi Sokongan: Jika masih tidak menerima TAC, lebih baik hubungi sokongan pelanggan untuk bantuan lanjut.

languages.en: Why hasn't my deposit been credited yet?

detailed.en: If your deposit has not been credited, there may be several reasons. Please wait a few minutes for the system to process it. If it still does not appear, you can contact customer support via live chat with your transaction details. We are here to help! If you have uploaded the receipt and still have not received the deposit, there may be a slight delay in processing. Please wait between 3 to 10 minutes. If after that there is still no entry, you can send the receipt via live chat for us to check. If you mistakenly transferred to your own bank account, unfortunately, we cannot process a refund. However, you can still use the credited amount to play. Please ensure to top-up correctly by uploading the bank-in receipt through (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). After sending, wait between 3 to 10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not enter within 10 minutes, please contact us via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika deposit anda belum masuk, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Sila tunggu beberapa minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika masih tidak muncul, anda boleh hubungi sokongan pelanggan melalui live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda. Kami sedia membantu! Jika anda sudah upload resit dan masih belum menerima deposit, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan dalam proses. Sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit. Jika selepas itu masih tiada kemasukan, anda boleh hantarkan resit melalui live chat untuk kami semak. Kami sedia membantu! Jika anda tersalah transfer ke akaun bank sendiri, malangnya, kami tidak dapat memproses refund. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan jumlah yang telah dikreditkan untuk bermain. Sila pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul dengan mengupload resit bank-in melalui (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). Selepas menghantar, tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika kredit tidak masuk dalam masa 10 minit, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Kami sedia membantu!

question.text: What does AOS mean in the context of betting?
variations: Aos tu ap ya

languages.en: What does AOS mean in the context of betting?
languages.ms: Aos tu ap ya

detailed.en: AOS stands for Any Other Score, which refers to high scores that are not listed in the regular betting options. Examples of AOS scores include 5-0, 5-1, 5-2, 6-5, 3-7, 5-5, 6-6, and 10-10. Regardless of which team wins, if the final score is not on the list, it is counted as AOS. You can choose AOS in the Correct Score betting if you think the match will have an unexpected score.
detailed.ms: AOS bermaksud Any Other Score â€“ iaitu skor tinggi yang tidak disenaraikan dalam pilihan bet biasa. Contoh skor AOS: 5-0, 5-1, 5-2, 6-5, 3-7, 5-5, 6-6, 10-10. Tak kira pasukan mana yang menang, jika skor akhir tidak ada dalam senarai, ia dikira sebagai AOS. Boss boleh pilih AOS dalam pertaruhan Correct Score kalau rasa perlawanan akan ada skor luar jangka.

detailed.en: If your top-up status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait for 3-10 minutes for the transaction to be processed. detailed.en: If you win a prize from Lucky Spin, the credit will automatically be added to your wallet within 24 hours. question.text: What is the minimum amount required for withdrawal and how does the turnover requirement work?

languages.en: What is the minimum amount required for withdrawal and how does the turnover requirement work?
languages.ms: Apakah jumlah minimum yang diperlukan untuk pengeluaran dan bagaimana syarat turnover berfungsi?

detailed.en: The minimum amount for withdrawal is RM30. You need to achieve a 30% turnover of your capital before you are eligible to withdraw. For example, if you top up RM100, you need to reach a turnover of RM130 (which is RM100 + 30%) before you can withdraw. If your balance is less than RM30, you need to accumulate more before you can withdraw.
detailed.ms: Jumlah minimum untuk pengeluaran adalah RM30. Anda perlu mencapai 30% turnover daripada modal sebelum layak untuk mengeluarkan. Sebagai contoh, jika anda top-up RM100, anda perlu mencapai turnover RM130 (iaitu RM100 + 30%) sebelum boleh mengeluarkan. Jika baki anda kurang daripada RM30, anda perlu mengumpul lagi sebelum boleh mengeluarkan.

detailed.en: If you have won a 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please check the app from time to time. If it has not been credited after 30 minutes, you can contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang nombor 4D, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses dan mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Duit kemenangan akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila semak aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa. Jika selepas 30 minit masih belum dikreditkan, anda boleh hubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan skrin resit dan keputusan.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up transaction is not reflected in the app?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up transaction is not reflected in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi top-up saya tidak dipaparkan dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: Hi boss, once you have topped up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. ğŸ˜Š After uploading, wait 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it still hasn't reflected after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, setelah anda topup, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi. ğŸ˜Š Selepas upload, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran bos!

question.text: What should I do to ensure a smooth top-up process using the banking app?

languages.en: What should I do to ensure a smooth top-up process using the banking app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk memastikan proses top-up berjalan lancar menggunakan aplikasi perbankan?

detailed.en: Please follow the list of banks provided in the app for your transfer. Ensure you use the account displayed on the top-up page to facilitate a smooth transaction. Do not save our bank account as a favorite, as the account number may change from time to time. If you have any other questions, feel free to contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Sila ikut senarai bank yang disediakan dalam aplikasi untuk pemindahan anda. Pastikan anda menggunakan akaun yang tertera pada halaman top-up untuk memudahkan transaksi berjalan lancar. Jangan simpan akaun bank kami sebagai kegemaran, kerana nombor akaun mungkin akan berubah dari semasa ke semasa. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang pertanyaan lain, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat.

question.text: What should I do if I am having trouble logging in to my account?
variations: How can I resolve login issues?
What steps can I take if I can't log in?

languages.en: What should I do if I am having trouble logging in to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah untuk log masuk ke akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues logging in, you can try the following steps: 1. Ensure that your username and password are correct. 2. Try clearing your browser's cache and cookies. 3. If you still cannot log in, try using a different browser or the mobile app. If you continue to have problems, please let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Pastikan nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda betul. 2. Cuba kosongkan cache dan cookies pelayar anda. 3. Jika masih tidak berjaya, cuba gunakan pelayar lain atau aplikasi mudah alih. Jika anda masih menghadapi masalah, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: What should I do if my payment has not been received after topping up via Fast Payment (FPX)?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment has not been received after topping up via Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pembayaran saya belum diterima selepas topup melalui Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: If you have topped up via Fast Payment (FPX) and it has been more than 10 minutes without the funds being received, please send a screenshot of the receipt and I will investigate immediately. Typically, the funds should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds are still not received, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah topup melalui Fast Payment (FPX) dan sudah lebih dari 10 minit tanpa dana diterima, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit dan saya akan siasat dengan segera. Biasanya, dana akan dikreditkan dalam 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan dana masih belum diterima, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan lanjut.

question.text: Why is my top-up taking longer than usual to process?
variations: Why is my top-up slow?
Why is my transaction delayed?

languages.en: Why is my top-up taking longer than usual to process?
languages.ms: Mengapa top-up saya mengambil masa lebih lama daripada biasa untuk diproses?

detailed.en: Top-ups are usually credited automatically within 5 to 30 minutes, but sometimes it can take longer due to high transaction volumes. If your winnings have not been credited within that time frame, please be patient or contact live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Top-up biasanya akan dikreditkan secara automatik dalam masa 5 hingga 30 minit, tetapi kadang-kadang ia boleh mengambil masa lebih lama disebabkan oleh jumlah transaksi yang tinggi. Jika kemenangan anda belum dikreditkan dalam tempoh itu, sila bersabar atau hubungi sokongan live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited yet?
variations: Bos top Up belom masok
What to do if top-up is delayed?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat support for further inspection. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantarkan resit transaksi lengkap kepada sokongan live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited yet?
variations: Belum masuk
Nanti Singapore tutup

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dimasukkan?

detailed.en: If your winnings have not been credited yet, please wait around 10 minutes for the system to process it. If it still does not appear, please contact live chat support with your transaction details. I hope it gets resolved quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan anda belum dimasukkan, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda. Semoga cepat selesai!

question.text: Saya terlupa untuk mengambil screenshot resit setelah melakukan pemindahan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: lupa ss tu resit
sya ada tf td tp sy lupa screenshot tu resit

languages.ms: Saya terlupa untuk mengambil screenshot resit setelah melakukan pemindahan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have made a transfer but forgot to include the reference number, you can upload the complete transaction receipt on the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait between 3-10 minutes for the system to verify. If after 10 minutes the funds still have not entered, please contact us via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah melakukan pemindahan tetapi terlupa untuk sertakan nombor rujukan, anda boleh muat naik resit transaksi yang lengkap di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Selepas muat naik, tunggu antara 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika selepas 10 minit dana masih belum masuk, sila hubungi kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What are the chances of winning a jackpot today?

languages.en: What are the chances of winning a jackpot today?
languages.ms: Apakah peluang untuk memenangi jackpot hari ini?

detailed.en: The chances of winning a jackpot can vary based on the game and the odds associated with it. However, it's always good to stay positive and hopeful for a win!
detailed.ms: Peluang untuk memenangi jackpot boleh berbeza-beza bergantung kepada permainan dan peluang yang berkaitan. Namun, adalah baik untuk sentiasa positif dan berharap untuk menang!

question.text: Apakah status jualan untuk Tuan Nom 6435?
variations: sold sdh kha nom tu tuan?
tuang nom 6435 sold sdh kha?

languages.en: What is the sale status for Tuan Nom 6435?
languages.ms: Apakah status jualan untuk Tuan Nom 6435?

detailed.en: I'm sorry, but I cannot provide specific information about the sale status of Tuan Nom 6435. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Maaf, tetapi saya tidak dapat memberikan maklumat spesifik tentang status jualan Tuan Nom 6435. Jika anda ada pertanyaan lain atau perlukan bantuan lanjut, jangan ragu untuk tanya!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up is still pending after 15 minutes?
variations: What to do if top-up is pending?
How long does it take for a top-up to process?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up is still pending after 15 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya masih pending selepas 15 minit?

detailed.en: If your top-up is still pending after 15 minutes, there may be an issue with the processing. Please check your transaction records in the app. If it still shows as Pending, send a screenshot of the receipt to us in live chat. We will check and ensure everything is running smoothly for you. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda masih pending selepas 15 minit, mungkin ada masalah dalam pemprosesan. Sila semak rekod transaksi anda dalam aplikasi. Jika masih dalam status Pending, hantar tangkapan layar resit kepada kami di live chat. Kami akan bantu semak dan pastikan semuanya berjalan lancar untuk anda. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: Why can't I top up my credit in the game?
variations: Kenapa mega tk boleh top up kredit?
Duit sy sudah ada dlm ewellet... Bila top up dlm game tk blh kenapa?
Sy dah transfer kenapa x masuk?
Sy top up dlm game xblh sbb apa?

languages.en: Why can't I top up my credit in the game?
languages.ms: Kenapa mega tk boleh top up kredit?

detailed.en: If you have money in your e-wallet but the top-up in the game is unsuccessful, ensure that you have uploaded the receipt correctly on the top-up page of the app. Wait between 3 to 10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If it still does not appear after that, please send the receipt via live chat for further assistance. Additionally, if you have already made a transfer but the top-up has not entered, check if you are using the correct transfer method such as ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). If it takes more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your transaction via live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika duit sudah ada dalam e-wallet tetapi top-up dalam permainan tidak berjaya, pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit dengan betul di halaman top-up aplikasi. Tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika selepas itu masih tidak muncul, sila hantarkan resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika anda sudah membuat pemindahan tetapi top-up masih belum masuk, semak sama ada anda menggunakan kaedah pemindahan yang betul seperti ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX). Jika ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, sila hantarkan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda melalui live chat untuk pengesahan lanjut.

question.text: What does 'tq bos' mean and how can I respond to it?
variations: What is the meaning of 'tq bos'?
How should I reply to 'tq bos'?

languages.en: What does 'tq bos' mean and how can I respond to it?
languages.ms: Apa maksud 'tq bos' dan bagaimana saya boleh membalasnya?

detailed.en: The phrase 'tq bos' is a casual way of saying 'thank you, boss' in Malay. A suitable response could be 'Sama-sama, boss!' which means 'You're welcome, boss!' and you can add a positive wish like 'Semoga anda dapat banyak ONG dan HUAT hari ini!' which translates to 'I hope you have a lot of good fortune today!'
detailed.ms: Frasa 'tq bos' adalah cara santai untuk mengatakan 'terima kasih, bos' dalam bahasa Melayu. Jawapan yang sesuai boleh menjadi 'Sama-sama, bos!' yang bermaksud 'Sama-sama, bos!' dan anda boleh menambah harapan positif seperti 'Semoga anda dapat banyak ONG dan HUAT hari ini!' yang diterjemahkan kepada 'Saya harap anda mempunyai banyak tuah hari ini!'

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do if my status shows PENDING and I am unable to access my account?
variations: Why is my status PENDING?
How can I resolve the PENDING status issue?

languages.en: What should I do if my status shows PENDING and I am unable to access my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status saya menunjukkan PENDING dan saya tidak dapat mengakses akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up of 10 has not been credited yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up of 10 has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya sebanyak 10 belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. If it still hasn't appeared after 10 minutes, please send your complete transaction receipt via live chat for immediate verification. We will assist in processing it as quickly as possible.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum muncul, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap anda melalui live chat untuk semakan segera. Kami akan bantu proses secepat mungkin.
