question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been processed after uploading the receipt?
variations: What happens if my top-up is delayed?
How long should I wait for my top-up to be confirmed?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been processed after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum diproses selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been processed, you only need to upload the receipt once and wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will take longer to process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't been processed, you should send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Please be patient, the system will process it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum diproses, anda hanya perlu memuat naik resit sekali sahaja dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika anda memuat naik resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan menolak transaksi dan ia akan mengambil masa lebih lama untuk diproses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan ia masih belum diproses, anda harus menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk pengesahan segera. Mohon bersabar, sistem akan memprosesnya secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been processed yet?
variations: What to do if my top-up is not showing?
How long does it take for a top-up to reflect?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been processed yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum diproses?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues with a top-up that has not been processed, please follow these steps: 1. Ensure you have uploaded the receipt only once and wait 1-10 minutes for system processing. 2. If you have trouble taking a screenshot, try logging back into your banking app and check your transaction history for the necessary details. 3. If the credit still does not appear after 10 minutes, please send your transaction details to live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah dengan top-up yang belum diproses, sila ikut langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit hanya sekali dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk pemprosesan sistem. 2. Jika anda menghadapi masalah untuk mengambil tangkapan skrin, cuba log masuk ke aplikasi bank anda semula dan semak sejarah transaksi untuk mendapatkan butiran yang diperlukan. 3. Jika selepas 10 minit kredit masih tidak muncul, sila hantarkan butiran transaksi kepada sokongan live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What does it mean if the status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What does it mean if the status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa maksudnya jika status menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: How can I invite new members to earn commissions?
variations: Is there a way to invite people for commissions?
What are the steps to invite friends for commissions?

languages.en: How can I invite new members to earn commissions?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh mengundang ahli baru untuk mendapatkan komisyen?

detailed.en: To invite new members and earn commissions, follow these steps: 1. Go to 'Profile' in the app. 2. Copy your 'Referral Link' from your profile. 3. Send that link to your friends for them to register. 4. Your friends can use that link to register and start playing. The referral link is only available in your own account in the app. If you have any issues or need assistance, please reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms: Untuk mengundang ahli baru dan mendapatkan komisyen, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke 'Profil' dalam aplikasi. 2. Salin 'Pautan Rujukan' dari profil anda. 3. Hantar pautan itu kepada rakan anda untuk mendaftar. 4. Rakan anda boleh menggunakan pautan tersebut untuk mendaftar dan mula bermain. Pautan Rujukan hanya tersedia dalam akaun anda sendiri dalam aplikasi. Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up via Fast Payment (FPX) is delayed?
variations: Why is my top-up taking so long?
How long should I wait for my top-up to process?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up via Fast Payment (FPX) is delayed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya melalui Fast Payment (FPX) tertangguh?

detailed.en: If your top-up via Fast Payment (FPX) is delayed, please wait for about 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, it should reflect within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the amount has not been credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda melalui Fast Payment (FPX) tertangguh, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, ia akan masuk dalam 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan jumlah belum dikreditkan, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do if I encounter issues with my wallet upload?

languages.en: What should I do if I encounter issues with my wallet upload?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah dengan muat naik dompet saya?

detailed.en: The receipt this time is the same as the one uploaded earlier. Please check your wallet.
detailed.ms: Resit kali ini sama dengan yang dimuat naik sebelum ini. Sila semak dompet anda.

question.text: What should I do if my transfer has not been credited after more than 5 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my transfer has not been credited after more than 5 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pemindahan saya belum dikreditkan selepas lebih dari 5 minit?

detailed.en: If your transfer has not been credited after more than 5 minutes, please wait as the process usually takes 3-10 minutes. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, send your full transaction details to live chat for a quick check.
detailed.ms: Jika pemindahan anda belum dikreditkan selepas lebih dari 5 minit, sila tunggu kerana proses biasanya mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika ia belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit, hantarkan butiran transaksi penuh anda ke live chat untuk semakan cepat.

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure the transaction is processed?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure the transaction is processed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai akaun saya untuk memastikan transaksi diproses?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Why hasn't my top-up been processed yet?
variations: knpa blm masuk sy topup

languages.en: Why hasn't my top-up been processed yet?
languages.ms: knpa blm masuk sy topup

detailed.en: I understand, boss! After you upload the receipt, the system usually takes 3-10 minutes to process the top-up. If the funds still do not appear after that period, please check whether you are using ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). If you are using FPX and it takes more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your transaction through live chat support for further verification.
detailed.ms: Faham, boss! Selepas anda muat naik resit, biasanya sistem memerlukan masa 3-10 minit untuk memproses top-up. Jika selepas tempoh itu dana masih tidak muncul, sila semak sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Pembayaran Pantas (FPX). Jika menggunakan FPX dan ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, sila hantarkan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda melalui sokongan live chat untuk pengesahan lanjut.

question.text: Saya ingin tahu tentang status duit yang saya masukkan, kenapa ia belum masuk?
variations: Duit yang saya masukkan sudah masuk ke akaun saya?
Kenapa duit yang saya masukkan belum diproses?

languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu tentang status duit yang saya masukkan, kenapa ia belum masuk?

detailed.ms: Faham, boss! Jika duit yang anda masukkan belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa antara 1 hingga 10 minit untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih dari itu, mungkin ada masalah lain. Boleh berikan saya lebih banyak maklumat tentang transaksi anda?

question.text: How do I upload my bank slip for the top-up process?

languages.en: How do I upload my bank slip for the top-up process?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh memuat naik slip bank saya untuk proses top-up?

detailed.en: To upload your bank slip, please go to the WALLET section and select TOPUP. The process will take approximately 3-5 minutes. Thank you for your cooperation!
detailed.ms: Untuk memuat naik slip bank anda, sila pergi ke bahagian WALLET dan pilih TOPUP. Proses ini akan mengambil masa kira-kira 3-5 minit. Terima kasih atas kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup akaun saya untuk memastikan transaksi saya diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Selepas topup, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: What should I do if I am unable to log in to my account?

languages.en: What should I do if I am unable to log in to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat log masuk ke akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues logging in, you can try the following steps: [steps]. If you need anything else, please let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: [steps]. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang anda perlukan, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: How can I top up my Touch 'n Go eWallet, and what are the available methods for doing so?

languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up eWallet Touch 'n Go saya, dan apakah kaedah yang tersedia untuk melakukannya?

detailed.en: To top up using Touch 'n Go (TNG), there are two methods: 1. ATM/Transfer (Min RM10) - Use DuitNow Transfer: Open the TNG eWallet, select DuitNow Transfer, enter the company account number, input the correct amount, and confirm the transaction. Take a screenshot of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app. This process takes 3-10 minutes for verification. 2. Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50) - Faster: Go to the top-up page in the app, select Fast Payment (FPX) and choose Touch 'n Go eWallet, enter the top-up amount, and confirm the transaction in the TNG eWallet. Funds will be credited automatically within 1-3 minutes. Note: ATM/Transfer requires manual receipt upload, while Fast Payment is quicker and automatic but has a minimum of RM50.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG), ada dua cara: 1. ATM/Transfer (Min RM10) - Gunakan DuitNow Transfer: Buka eWallet TNG, pilih DuitNow Transfer, masukkan nombor akaun syarikat, masukkan jumlah yang betul dan sahkan transaksi. Ambil tangkapan skrin resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Proses ini mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. 2. Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50) - Lebih cepat: Pergi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, pilih Fast Payment (FPX) dan pilih eWallet Touch 'n Go, masukkan jumlah top-up dan sahkan transaksi dalam eWallet TNG. Dana akan dikreditkan secara automatik dalam 1-3 minit. Nota: ATM/Transfer memerlukan muat naik resit secara manual, manakala Fast Payment lebih cepat dan automatik tetapi mempunyai minimum RM50.

question.text: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure the receipt is processed quickly?
variations: What details are needed for an online transfer?
How can I ensure my online transfer receipt is confirmed quickly?

languages.en: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure the receipt is processed quickly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya sertakan semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian untuk memastikan resit diproses dengan cepat?

detailed.en: When making an online transfer, please ensure to fill in your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field along with other payment details. This is crucial for us to verify the receipt quickly.
detailed.ms: Semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian, sila pastikan untuk mengisi ID JOKER anda dalam ruangan 'Reference Penerima' bersama dengan butiran pembayaran lain. Ini adalah penting untuk kami mengesahkan resit dengan cepat.

question.text: What should I do after topping up RM100 to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah RM100 untuk memastikan transaksi saya diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If the funds are not credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt via live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: User is asking about the process to enter work and whether they have completed the necessary steps.
variations: Sudah kah boss saya nak masok kerja ni

languages.en: User is asking about the process to enter work and whether they have completed the necessary steps.
languages.ms: User sedang bertanya tentang proses untuk masuk kerja dan sama ada mereka telah menyelesaikan langkah-langkah yang diperlukan.

detailed.en: Hi boss, once you have topped up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hi boss, setelah anda topup, pastikan resit telah diupload ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi. Selepas upload, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika lebih dari 10 minit masih belum diproses, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: How can I top up RM200 and what should I do if the funds are not credited after 10 minutes?
variations: What steps should I follow to top up RM200?
What to do if my RM200 top-up is not credited?

languages.en: How can I top up RM200 and what should I do if the funds are not credited after 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top-up RM200 dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika dana tidak dikreditkan selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: To top up RM200, ensure you have uploaded the receipt on the top-up page in the app. Wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If the funds are still not credited after 10 minutes, please send the receipt via live chat for assistance. If you used Touch 'n Go/BANK, let me know if you used ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX) so I can help check for you.
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up RM200, pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika dana masih belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit, sila hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan. Jika anda menggunakan Touch 'n Go/BANK, beritahu saya jika anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX) supaya saya boleh bantu semak untuk anda.

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally uploaded the same receipt twice?
variations: I uploaded the same receipt twice, what now?
What happens if I double upload a receipt?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally uploaded the same receipt twice?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya secara tidak sengaja memuat naik resit yang sama dua kali?

detailed.en: If you have submitted two receipts, the system only requires one receipt for verification. Submitting the same receipt multiple times may cause the system to reject your application. Please wait 3-10 minutes for processing. If there are any issues, feel free to reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menghantar dua resit, sistem hanya memerlukan satu resit untuk semakan. Menghantar resit yang sama berkali-kali boleh menyebabkan sistem menolak permohonan anda. Sila tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pemprosesan. Jika ada sebarang masalah, jangan ragu untuk balas kepada kami dalam live chat.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: Please let me know if you are using ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX) for the top-up. This will help me check the status for you.
detailed.ms: Sila beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX) untuk top-up. Ini akan membantu saya menyemak status untuk anda.

question.text: What are the transactions that have not been processed yet, such as top-up, withdrawal, or game credit?

languages.en: What are the transactions that have not been processed yet, such as top-up, withdrawal, or game credit?
languages.ms: Apakah transaksi yang belum diproses, seperti top-up, pengeluaran, atau kredit permainan?

detailed.en: To assist you better, could you please specify whether the transactions that have not been processed are related to top-up, withdrawal, or game credit?
detailed.ms: Untuk membantu anda dengan lebih baik, bolehkah anda menyatakan sama ada transaksi yang belum diproses berkaitan dengan top-up, pengeluaran, atau kredit permainan?

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited to my account?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dimasukkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes after uploading the receipt. If the funds still do not appear, please contact live chat support with your complete receipt. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika dana masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: Why is the transaction taking so long, and what should I do if it shows as pending?
variations: Why is it taking so long?
What does pending status mean?
How long should I wait for my transaction?

languages.en: Why is the transaction taking so long, and what should I do if it shows as pending?
languages.ms: Kenapa transaksi mengambil masa yang lama, dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika ia menunjukkan status pending?

detailed.en: If your top-up is still not processed, there may be a slight delay. Typically, it takes between 3 to 10 minutes. If it has been more than that, please send a screenshot of your transaction receipt, and I will assist you immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda masih belum diproses, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan. Biasanya, ia mengambil masa antara 3 hingga 10 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit transaksi anda, dan saya akan bantu semak dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do if my status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What should I do if my status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status saya menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?

detailed.en: If your status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: After topping up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds will be credited within 1 to 10 minutes. If the funds do not appear after 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, dana akan dikreditkan dalam masa 1 hingga 10 minit. Jika dana tidak muncul selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: I have been transferring money to my Maybank account but it hasn't been credited. What could be the issue?
variations: Why hasn't my transfer to Maybank been credited?
What should I check if my Maybank transfer is not showing up?

languages.en: I have been transferring money to my Maybank account but it hasn't been credited. What could be the issue?
languages.ms: Saya telah memindahkan wang ke akaun Maybank saya tetapi ia belum dikreditkan. Apa masalahnya?

detailed.en: If you have transferred from RHB to Maybank and it hasn't been credited, please check the following: 1ï¸âƒ£ Ensure you have entered the correct account number. 2ï¸âƒ£ Sometimes, there may be delays in the banking system that can cause transactions to be slow. If it has been more than 30 minutes and there is still no credit, I recommend contacting RHB or Maybank customer service for further information about the transaction.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memindahkan dari RHB ke Maybank dan ia masih belum masuk, sila semak: 1ï¸âƒ£ Pastikan anda telah memasukkan nombor akaun yang betul. 2ï¸âƒ£ Kadang-kadang, ada kelewatan dalam sistem bank yang boleh menyebabkan transaksi lambat. Jika sudah lebih dari 30 minit dan masih tiada kemasukan, saya sarankan anda hubungi khidmat pelanggan RHB atau Maybank untuk mendapatkan maklumat lanjut tentang transaksi tersebut.

question.text: Is there an alternative account number available for transactions?
variations: tkde nombor akaum lain ke

languages.en: Is there an alternative account number available for transactions?
languages.ms: tkde nombor akaum lain ke

detailed.en: If you have uploaded the receipt, please wait 3-10 minutes for the system to credit the funds to your account. If the funds have not been credited after 10 minutes, please contact live chat for immediate assistance. You will be able to purchase numbers for the 9 PM draw once your account is credited. If you need anything else, let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah upload resit, tunggu dalam 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengkreditkan dana ke akaun anda. Jika selepas 10 minit dana masih belum masuk, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Anda akan dapat membeli nombor untuk undian 9 malam setelah akaun anda dikreditkan. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang anda perlukan, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: How long do I need to wait for my transaction confirmation after uploading the receipt?
variations: lama lagi ke

languages.en: How long do I need to wait for my transaction confirmation after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: lama lagi ke

detailed.en: After uploading the receipt, you should wait for 1 to 10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If the funds have not been credited after 10 minutes, please send the transaction receipt via live chat for immediate assistance.
detailed.ms: Lepas upload, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: I have deposited RM10, but it has not been credited yet. What should I do?
variations: saya masok 10 blom msok lagi

languages.en: I have deposited RM10, but it has not been credited yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: saya masok 10 blom msok lagi

detailed.en: If you have deposited RM10 but it has not been credited yet, there may be a slight delay. Please wait for 3 to 10 minutes for confirmation. If the funds are still not credited, you can send the receipt via live chat for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah masukkan RM10 tetapi masih belum masuk, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan. Sila tunggu dalam 3 hingga 10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika masih tiada kemasukan, anda boleh hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: Why hasn't my payment been credited yet?
variations: bayaran saya belum masuk
kenapa bayaran saya belum diterima

languages.en: Why hasn't my payment been credited yet?
languages.ms: Kenapa bayaran saya belum diterima?

detailed.en: If your payment or top-up has not been credited, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes after uploading the receipt. If there is still no update, you can send a screenshot of the receipt to me, and I will assist you in checking it immediately. Additionally, if you have won a 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winning money will be credited to your wallet automatically, so please check the app from time to time. If it has been more than 30 minutes and it is still not credited, please contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika bayaran atau top-up anda belum masuk, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika masih tiada, boleh hantar tangkapan skrin resit kepada saya dan saya akan bantu semak dengan segera. Jika anda ada nombor 4D yang menang, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet anda secara automatik, sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam aplikasi. Jika lebih 30 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan skrin resit & keputusan.

question.text: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system, and what should I do while waiting for the process to complete?

languages.ms: Apa maksudnya apabila status menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem, dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan sementara menunggu proses selesai?

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it takes more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can send a message to live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika status menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghantar mesej ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Why hasn't the money been credited to my account yet?
variations: Duit belum masuk
Kenapa duit tak masuk lagi?

languages.en: Why hasn't the money been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Kenapa duit belum masuk ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If the money hasn't been credited yet, it usually takes more than 10 minutes. If it still hasn't arrived, please send a screenshot of the receipt and I will investigate it immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika duit belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit. Jika masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit dan saya akan siasat dengan segera. Terima kasih!

en: Is this related to a top-up, withdrawal, or game credit?
ms: Adakah ini berkaitan dengan topup, pengeluaran, atau kredit permainan?

question.text: I have topped up my account, but the amount has not been credited yet. What should I do?

languages.en: I have topped up my account, but the amount has not been credited yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya sudah top up tetapi jumlahnya belum dimasukkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have topped up and it hasn't been credited yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for further investigation. detailed.en: If you forget to enter the JOKER ID during the transfer, you can upload the transaction receipt as usual. Make sure the receipt is complete and clearly shows the transaction details. question.text: Can I use the Touch 'n Go e-wallet for transactions?
variations: Is the Touch 'n Go e-wallet usable?
Can I top up using Touch 'n Go?

languages.en: Can I use the Touch 'n Go e-wallet for transactions?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan e-wallet Touch 'n Go untuk transaksi?

detailed.en: To top up using the Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, follow these steps: 1. Open TNG eWallet and go to the 'Transfer' section. 2. Select DuitNow Transfer. 3. Enter our company's bank account number (refer to the top-up page). 4. Enter the correct amount (Min RM10 for ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 for Fast Payment). 5. Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the complete receipt. 6. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 7. Wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. Important: Ensure to use DuitNow Transfer (not regular eWallet transfer). The account owner's name must match the name in the app to avoid rejection. If there are any issues, reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up menggunakan e-wallet Touch 'n Go (TNG), ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka TNG eWallet dan pergi ke bahagian 'Transfer'. 2. Pilih DuitNow Transfer. 3. Masukkan nombor akaun bank syarikat kami (rujuk pada halaman top-up). 4. Masukkan jumlah yang betul (Min RM10 untuk ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 untuk Fast Payment). 5. Sahkan transaksi dan ambil tangkapan skrin resit yang lengkap. 6. Muat naik resit ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan di live chat. 7. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Penting: Pastikan menggunakan DuitNow Transfer (bukan transfer eWallet biasa). Nama pemilik akaun mesti sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi untuk mengelakkan penolakan. Jika ada masalah, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya.

question.text: What should I do if the ATM does not provide a receipt after making a deposit?

languages.en: What should I do if the ATM does not provide a receipt after making a deposit?

detailed.en: If the ATM does not produce a receipt after you make a deposit, you can take the following steps: 1. **Note transaction details**: Write down the method of transfer (ATM Card/Cash Deposit/Online), time of transfer, bank name, amount deposited, and sender's name. 2. **Contact support**: Please reach out to support via live chat and provide this information. This will help us verify your transaction. If you need anything else, let me know!

Ini akan membantu kami mengesahkan transaksi anda. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang anda perlukan, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: What should I do if my deposit is not processed?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit is not processed?

detailed.en: Deposits usually take between 5 to 30 minutes to be processed. If your deposit has failed, there may be an issue with the deposit method or receipt. question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited after more than 10 minutes?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited after more than 10 minutes, please ensure that you have uploaded the receipt to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it still does not appear after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate assistance. Thank you for your patience!

question.text: I have deposited RM50 but it has not been credited yet. What should I do?

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your deposit. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it may slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the issue persists, you can send a message to live chat for further assistance. Additionally, please upload your bank slip through (WALLET -> TOPUP). The process usually takes about 3-5 minutes.
detailed.ms: Jika status tunjuk PENDING, maksudnya sistem tengah proses sekarang ya. Mohon boss tunggu dulu sampai sistem selesai proses. question.text: What should I do if the kissme application is not opening?
variations: Kenapa kissme tak boleh main

languages.en: What should I do if the kissme application is not opening?
languages.ms: Kenapa kissme tak boleh main

detailed.en:
If kissme cannot be opened, try the following steps:

1. Close and reopen the kissme application.
2. Log out and log back into the Joker application, then try again.
3. Change your internet connection (try WiFi or mobile data).
4. Check if the game is under maintenance â€“ if so, wait until it is completed.
5. Try reinstalling the game using the correct link.

If the problem persists, send us a screenshot of the error in live chat so we can assist you further.
detailed.ms:
Jika kissme tak boleh dibuka, cuba langkah-langkah berikut:

1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi kissme.
2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam aplikasi Joker, kemudian cuba lagi.
3. Tukar sambungan internet (cuba WiFi atau data mudah alih).
4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan â€“ jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai.
5. Cuba pasang semula permainan menggunakan pautan yang betul.

Jika masalah masih berterusan, hantarkan tangkapan skrin ralat kepada kami di live chat supaya kami dapat membantu lebih lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up from Fast Payment (FPX) takes longer than expected to process?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up from Fast Payment (FPX) takes longer than expected to process?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika topup saya dari Fast Payment (FPX) mengambil masa lebih lama daripada yang dijangkakan untuk diproses?

detailed.en: If you have topped up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.

Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan dana belum dikreditkan, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: What should I do if I forget to include the JOKER ID during a transfer?

detailed.en: If you forget to include the JOKER ID during a transfer, don't worry! Hereâ€™s what you need to do: Ensure that the transaction receipt is complete and clear. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app as usual. Wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to verify the transaction. For next time, make sure to write the JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field so that the system can verify it faster. If you have any issues or need assistance, feel free to contact us via live chat!

Untuk lain kali, pastikan anda menulis ID JOKER di ruangan 'Rujukan Penerima' supaya sistem boleh mengesahkan lebih cepat. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat!

question.text: How can I claim the RM20 that I deposited? Is there a specific process I need to follow?

detailed.en: To claim the RM20, if you have already uploaded the receipt, please wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If it has not been credited yet, you can send the receipt via live chat. If your balance is only RM20 and you have made two deposits of RM20, there may be an issue with transaction confirmation. Usually, the confirmation process takes 3-10 minutes. If it has been longer than that and you still haven't received it, I recommend contacting customer service directly for immediate assistance.

Jika baki anda hanya RM20 dan anda telah membuat dua deposit RM20, mungkin ada masalah dengan pengesahan transaksi. Biasanya, proses pengesahan mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu dan anda masih belum menerimanya, saya sarankan anda menghubungi perkhidmatan pelanggan secara langsung untuk bantuan segera.

question.text: Can you help me change my mobile number as my current number is no longer active?

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan pengeluaran dan top-up di aplikasi Tesla?

languages.en: How to withdraw and top up in the Tesla app?
languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan pengeluaran dan top-up di aplikasi Tesla?

detailed.en: To withdraw, follow these steps in the app: 1. Click the 'Wallet' icon at the bottom center of the screen. 2. Select 'Withdraw'. 3. Ensure the selected bank account is marked as 'Primary'. 4. Enter the amount you wish to withdraw (Min RM10). 5. Click 'Submit' to send the withdrawal request. 6. Wait 5-30 minutes for the process to complete. For top-up in Tesla, you can follow these steps: 1. Use Instant Transfer or DuitNow (do not use IBG). 2. Enter the company account number and the amount you wish to add. 3. Add your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' if using online banking. 4. Upload the receipt on the top-up page in the app. 5. Wait 3-10 minutes for processing. Alternatively, for Fast Payment (FPX), go to the top-up page in the app, select FPX and your bank, enter the amount, and confirm the transaction. Wait 1-3 minutes for automatic confirmation.
detailed.ms: Untuk pengeluaran, ikut langkah-langkah ini dalam aplikasi: 1. Klik ikon 'Wallet' (di tengah bawah skrin). 2. Pilih 'Withdraw'. 3. Pastikan akaun bank yang dipilih mempunyai tanda 'Primary'. 4. Masukkan jumlah yang ingin dikeluarkan (Min RM10). 5. Klik 'Submit' untuk menghantar permohonan pengeluaran. 6. Tunggu 5-30 minit untuk proses selesai. Untuk top-up di Tesla, anda boleh ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Gunakan Instant Transfer atau DuitNow (âŒ Jangan gunakan IBG). 2. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat dan jumlah yang ingin ditambah. 3. Tambahkan JOKER ID anda dalam 'Recipient Reference' (jika menggunakan perbankan dalam talian). 4. Muat naik resit di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. 5. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk proses. Sebagai alternatif, untuk Pembayaran Pantas (FPX), pergi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, pilih FPX dan bank anda, masukkan jumlah dan sahkan transaksi. Tunggu 1-3 minit untuk pengesahan automatik.

Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan transaksi masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghantar mesej ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. languages.en: What are the options for withdrawing winnings of 100k?
languages.ms: Apakah pilihan untuk mengeluarkan kemenangan sebanyak 100k?

detailed.en: If you win with the number 100k, you have several options for withdrawal: 1. **Direct Transfer**: You can withdraw the full amount directly (the process usually takes 5-30 minutes). 2. **Partial Withdrawal**: You can split the withdrawal into smaller amounts for more flexibility. 3. **Use Company Account**: For winnings over 100k, you can choose to use a company account to 'wash' the funds, which facilitates processing for large amounts.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang dengan nombor 100k, anda mempunyai beberapa pilihan untuk pengeluaran: 1. **Pemindahan Langsung**: Anda boleh mengeluarkan jumlah penuh secara langsung (proses biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit). 2. **Pengeluaran Sebahagian**: Anda boleh membahagikan pengeluaran kepada jumlah yang lebih kecil untuk lebih fleksibiliti. 3. **Gunakan Akaun Syarikat**: Untuk kemenangan di atas 100k, anda boleh memilih untuk menggunakan akaun syarikat untuk 'mencuci' dana, yang memudahkan pemprosesan untuk jumlah besar.

question.text: How can I check if I have won in the 4D lottery?
variations: ada Sy menang nombor 4d ?

languages.en: How can I check if I have won in the 4D lottery?
languages.ms: ada Sy menang nombor 4d ?

detailed.en: To check if you have won in the 4D lottery, you can follow these steps: Open the JOKER App, tap on the 4D icon, select the Results menu, and compare your numbers and house with your receipt. If you have won, the winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet within 1-10 minutes after the results are processed. If your winnings have not been credited, feel free to contact live chat support for assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk menyemak jika anda telah menang dalam loteri 4D, anda boleh mengikuti langkah-langkah ini: Buka Aplikasi JOKER, tekan ikon 4D, pilih menu Keputusan, dan bandingkan nombor anda dan rumah dengan resit anda. Jika anda menang, kemenangan akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam wallet anda dalam masa 1-10 minit setelah keputusan diproses. Jika kemenangan anda belum dikreditkan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi sokongan live chat untuk bantuan.

question.text: Why can't I deposit using someone else's account?
variations: Knp tak boleh bank in pakai acc org lain

languages.en: Why can't I deposit using someone else's account?
languages.ms: Knp tak boleh bank in pakai acc org lain

detailed.en: You cannot make a deposit using someone else's account for security reasons. The receipt must come from your own account. If the name of the account owner does not match the name registered in the application, the transaction will be rejected. Please ensure you use your own account to avoid any issues!
detailed.ms: Maaf, boss, tetapi anda tidak boleh membuat deposit menggunakan akaun orang lain. Untuk keselamatan, resit perlu datang dari akaun anda sendiri. Jika nama pemilik akaun tidak sepadan dengan nama yang didaftarkan dalam aplikasi, transaksi akan ditolak. Pastikan anda menggunakan akaun anda sendiri untuk mengelakkan sebarang masalah!

question.text: How can I top up my Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet using e-wallet methods?

languages.en: How can I top up my Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet using e-wallet methods?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up e-wallet Touch 'n Go (TNG) menggunakan kaedah e-wallet?

detailed.en:
To top up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, there are two methods:

ğŸ”¹ **1ï¸âƒ£ ATM/Transfer (Min RM10)** - Use DuitNow Transfer
- Open TNG eWallet, select DuitNow Transfer.
- Enter the company account number (refer to the top-up page).
- Enter the correct amount and confirm the transaction.
- Take a screenshot of the receipt & upload it to the top-up page in the app.
- The process takes 3-10 minutes for verification.

ğŸ”¹ **2ï¸âƒ£ Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50)** - Faster
- Go to the top-up page in the app.
- Select Fast Payment (FPX) and choose Touch 'n Go eWallet.
- Enter the top-up amount & confirm the transaction in TNG eWallet.
- Funds will be credited automatically within 1-3 minutes.

ğŸ“Œ **Important:**
- ATM/Transfer with DuitNow requires manual receipt upload.
- Fast Payment (FPX) is faster & automatic, but the minimum is RM50.

If you have any questions, reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, ada dua cara:

ğŸ”¹ **1ï¸âƒ£ ATM/Transfer (Min RM10)** - Gunakan DuitNow Transfer
- Buka TNG eWallet, pilih DuitNow Transfer.
- Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat (rujuk pada halaman top-up).
- Masukkan jumlah yang betul dan sahkan transaksi.
- Ambil tangkapan skrin resit & muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
- Proses mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan.

ğŸ”¹ **2ï¸âƒ£ Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50)** - Lebih cepat
- Pergi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
- Pilih Fast Payment (FPX) dan pilih Touch 'n Go eWallet.
- Masukkan jumlah top-up & sahkan transaksi dalam TNG eWallet.
- Dana akan dikreditkan secara automatik dalam 1-3 minit.

ğŸ“Œ **Penting:**
- ATM/Transfer dengan DuitNow memerlukan muat naik resit secara manual.
- Fast Payment (FPX) lebih cepat & automatik, tetapi minimum RM50.

Jika ada soalan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat!

question.text: What should I do if my deposit has not been credited yet?
variations: Why hasn't my deposit appeared?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your deposit status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the deposit is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika status deposit anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan deposit masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What are the alternative methods for topping up if Fast Payment (FPX) through Touch 'n Go is under maintenance?

languages.en: What are the alternative methods for topping up if Fast Payment (FPX) through Touch 'n Go is under maintenance?
languages.ms: Apakah kaedah alternatif untuk menambah nilai jika Fast Payment (FPX) melalui Touch 'n Go sedang dalam penyelenggaraan?

detailed.en: Currently, Fast Payment (FPX) through Touch 'n Go is under maintenance. You can try other methods for topping up: ATM/Transfer (DuitNow / Instant Transfer) with a minimum of RM10, or Fast Payment (FPX) through other banks with a minimum of RM50. If you still encounter issues or need assistance, feel free to contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Ketika ini, Fast Payment (FPX) melalui Touch 'n Go sedang dalam penyelenggaraan. Anda boleh mencuba kaedah lain untuk menambah nilai: ATM/Transfer (DuitNow / Instant Transfer) dengan minimum RM10, atau Fast Payment (FPX) melalui bank lain dengan minimum RM50. Jika anda masih menghadapi masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat.

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal has not been processed yet?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran saya belum diproses?

detailed.en: If you have made a withdrawal, you can check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the funds have not arrived, you can send the transaction details to live chat for immediate verification. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it still hasn't arrived, send the transaction details to live chat for immediate assistance. We will help verify for you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat pengeluaran, anda boleh semak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan dana belum tiba, anda boleh hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Juga, semak dalam wallet untuk melihat jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum tiba, hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk bantuan segera. Kami akan bantu semak untuk anda!

question.text: I have already topped up my Touch 'n Go (TNG) wallet, but the money is not showing up. What should I do?

languages.en: I have already topped up my Touch 'n Go (TNG) wallet, but the money is not showing up. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya sudah top up dompet Touch 'n Go (TNG), tetapi duit tidak muncul. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en:
If you have topped up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) but the money is not in your wallet, there are several steps you can try:

1. If you used Fast Payment (FPX):
   - Ensure you selected TNG eWallet in the payment section.
   - Wait 1-3 minutes for the system to automatically verify the transaction.
   - If after 3 minutes there is still no money, please send the FPX transaction receipt to live chat for further checking.

2. If you used DuitNow Transfer:
   - Make sure you selected DuitNow to the bank account number, not a regular eWallet transfer.
   - Manually upload the transaction receipt to the top-up page in the app.
   - Wait 3-10 minutes for system verification.

If you still have issues, try:
- Switching your internet connection (WiFi/Data).
- Checking if TNG is undergoing maintenance.
- Trying other methods like ATM/Transfer.

If it still doesn't work, please reply to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms:
Jika anda telah top up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) tetapi masih tidak ada duit dalam dompet, mungkin ada beberapa langkah yang boleh dicuba:

1. Jika anda menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX):
   - Pastikan anda memilih TNG eWallet dalam bahagian pembayaran.
   - Tunggu 1-3 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi secara automatik.
   - Jika selepas 3 minit masih tiada, sila hantar resit transaksi FPX ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut.

2. Jika anda menggunakan DuitNow Transfer:
   - Pastikan anda memilih DuitNow ke nombor akaun bank, bukan pemindahan eWallet biasa.
   - Muat naik resit transaksi secara manual ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
   - Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan sistem.

Jika masih ada masalah, cuba:
- Tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi/Data).
- Semak jika TNG sedang dalam penyelenggaraan.
- Cuba kaedah lain seperti ATM/Pindahan.

Jika masih tidak berjaya, balas kepada kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut ya.

question.text: What do the terms 4A, 4B, and 4C mean in the context of 4D betting?
variations: bole tanya ..apa maksud 4A 4B 4C

languages.en: What do the terms 4A, 4B, and 4C mean in the context of 4D betting?
languages.ms: bole tanya ..apa maksud 4A 4B 4C

detailed.en: In 4D betting, the meanings are as follows: 4A is exclusive to the first prize number, offering the highest payout but with the lowest chance of winning. 4B covers the first and second prize numbers, providing better odds than 4A. 4C includes the first, second, and third prize numbers, giving higher chances of winning compared to both 4A and 4B.
detailed.ms: Dalam pertaruhan 4D, maksudnya adalah seperti berikut: 4A adalah eksklusif untuk nombor hadiah pertama, menawarkan pembayaran tertinggi tetapi dengan peluang menang yang paling rendah. 4B meliputi nombor hadiah pertama dan kedua, memberikan peluang yang lebih baik berbanding 4A. 4C termasuk nombor hadiah pertama, kedua, dan ketiga, memberikan peluang menang yang lebih tinggi berbanding 4A dan 4B.

variations: How do I top-up via bank transfer?

languages.ms: Apakah proses untuk melengkapkan top-up melalui pemindahan bank dan berapa lama masa yang diambil untuk dana muncul?

detailed.en: To complete a top-up via bank transfer, follow these steps: For ATM/Transfer (minimum RM10), use Instant Transfer or DuitNow (do not use IBG), enter the company account number and amount, add your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' if using online banking, upload the receipt on the top-up page in the app, and wait 3-10 minutes for processing. For Fast Payment (FPX, minimum RM50, faster), go to the top-up page in the app, select FPX and your preferred bank, enter the amount and confirm the transaction, and wait 1-3 minutes for automatic confirmation. Ensure the bank account name matches the name registered in the app. If there are issues, respond to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk melengkapkan top-up melalui pemindahan bank, ikut langkah-langkah ini: Untuk ATM/Transfer (Min RM10), gunakan Instant Transfer atau DuitNow (jangan gunakan IBG), masukkan nombor akaun syarikat dan amaun, tambah JOKER ID anda dalam 'Recipient Reference' jika menggunakan perbankan dalam talian, muat naik resit di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pemprosesan. Untuk Fast Payment (FPX, Min RM50, lebih cepat), pergi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, pilih FPX dan bank pilihan anda, masukkan amaun dan sahkan transaksi, dan tunggu 1-3 minit untuk pengesahan automatik. Pastikan nama akaun bank sepadan dengan nama yang didaftarkan dalam aplikasi. Jika ada masalah, balas kepada kami dalam live chat.

question.text: What should I do if all the games keep getting stuck during loading?

languages.en: What should I do if all the games keep getting stuck during loading?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika semua permainan asyik sangkut semasa memuat?

detailed.en:
To resolve the issue of long loading times when logging in, you can try the following steps:

1. Close and reopen the game app.
2. Logout and log back into the Joker App, then re-enter your ID and Password.
3. Change your internet connection (try WiFi or mobile data).
4. Check if the game is under maintenance â€“ if it is, wait until it is completed.
5. If you still cannot access the game, try using a VPN:
   - Download a VPN for Malaysia from the link provided.
   - Install the VPN and open the application.
   - Tap "Connect to Malaysia" and wait until the connection is successful.
   - After connecting, try logging back into the game.

If the problem persists, you can send a screenshot to live chat for immediate assistance.
detailed.ms:
Untuk menyelesaikan masalah masa muat yang lama semasa log masuk, anda boleh mencuba langkah-langkah berikut:

1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi permainan.
2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam Aplikasi Joker, kemudian masukkan semula ID dan Kata Laluan anda.
3. Tukar sambungan internet anda (cuba WiFi atau data mudah alih).
4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan - jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai.
5. Jika anda masih tidak dapat mengakses permainan, cuba gunakan VPN:
   - Muat turun VPN untuk Malaysia dari pautan yang diberikan.
   - Pasang VPN dan buka aplikasi.
   - Tekan "Sambung ke Malaysia" dan tunggu sehingga sambungan berjaya.
   - Selepas menyambung, cuba log masuk semula ke permainan.

Jika masalah berterusan, anda boleh menghantar tangkapan skrin ke live chat untuk bantuan segera.

Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not completed, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status transaksi anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum selesai, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if I am experiencing issues with logging in or topping up my wallet?

detailed.en: To resolve login issues, please follow these steps: [steps]. If you need to top up your wallet, please upload your bank-in slip through (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). The process will take about 3-10 minutes for the system to verify the transaction. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, please send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Untuk menyelesaikan masalah log masuk, sila ikuti langkah-langkah berikut: [langkah-langkah]. Jika anda perlu menambah nilai dompet anda, sila muat naik slip bank-in anda melalui (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). Proses ini akan mengambil masa sekitar 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit, sila hantarkan resit transaksi ke live chat untuk pengesahan segera.

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk top up menggunakan Touch 'n Go eWallet?
variations: macam mana topup guna touch n go

languages.en: How to top up using Touch 'n Go eWallet?
languages.ms: Macam mana cara untuk top up menggunakan Touch 'n Go eWallet?

detailed.en: To top up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, follow these steps: 1. Open TNG eWallet and go to the 'Transfer' section. 2. Select DuitNow Transfer. 3. Enter our company's bank account number (refer to the top-up page). 4. Enter the correct amount (Min RM10 for ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 for Fast Payment). 5. Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the complete receipt. 6. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 7. Wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. Important: Ensure to use DuitNow Transfer (not regular eWallet transfer). The account owner's name must match the name in the app to avoid rejection. If you have any issues, reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka TNG eWallet dan pergi ke bahagian 'Transfer'. 2. Pilih DuitNow Transfer. 3. Masukkan nombor akaun bank syarikat kami (rujuk pada halaman top-up). 4. Masukkan jumlah yang betul (Min RM10 untuk ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 untuk Fast Payment). 5. Sahkan transaksi dan ambil tangkapan skrin resit yang lengkap. 6. Muat naik resit ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan di live chat. 7. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Penting: Pastikan menggunakan DuitNow Transfer (bukan pemindahan eWallet biasa). Nama pemilik akaun mesti sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi untuk mengelakkan penolakan. Jika ada sebarang masalah, balas kepada kami di live chat.

question.text: Can I use Touch 'n Go (TNG) for top-up transactions?
variations: kalau guna tng boleh ke boss
kalau guna tng boleh ke?

languages.en: Can I use Touch 'n Go (TNG) for top-up transactions?
languages.ms: kalau guna tng boleh ke boss

detailed.en: If you want to top-up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet and it is not working, try the following steps: Ensure you are using the correct method. If using Fast Payment (FPX), make sure to select TNG eWallet in the payment section and wait 1-3 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction automatically. If not credited after 3 minutes, send the FPX transaction receipt to live chat for verification. If using DuitNow Transfer via TNG, ensure you select DuitNow to the bank account number, not a regular eWallet transfer. Upload the transaction receipt manually to the top-up page in the app and wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If there are still issues, try changing your internet connection, check if TNG is under maintenance, or try another method like ATM/Transfer. If it still doesn't work, contact us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda ingin top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet dan ia tidak berfungsi, cuba langkah-langkah berikut: Pastikan anda menggunakan kaedah yang betul. Jika menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), pastikan anda memilih TNG eWallet dalam bahagian pembayaran dan tunggu 1-3 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi secara automatik. Jika tidak dikreditkan selepas 3 minit, hantarkan resit transaksi FPX ke live chat untuk semakan. Jika menggunakan DuitNow Transfer melalui TNG, pastikan anda memilih DuitNow ke nombor akaun bank, bukan pemindahan eWallet biasa. Muat naik resit transaksi secara manual ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika masih ada masalah, cuba tukar rangkaian internet, semak jika TNG sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, atau cuba kaedah lain seperti ATM/Transfer. Jika masih tidak berjaya, balas kepada kami dalam live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my RM400 top-up hasn't been credited to my account yet?
variations: Belum masuk rm400
I baru upload resit disini

languages.en: What should I do if my RM400 top-up hasn't been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up RM400 saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you have uploaded the receipt for the RM400 top-up but it has not been credited yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. If it has been more than that and it still hasn't appeared, please send me a screenshot of the receipt, and I will check it for you. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah upload resit untuk top-up RM400 tetapi masih belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih dari itu dan masih belum muncul, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit kepada saya, dan saya akan semak untuk anda. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally transfer money to my own bank account for the first time?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally transfer money to my own bank account for the first time?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah transfer wang ke akaun bank saya sendiri untuk kali pertama?

detailed.en: If you accidentally transfer money to your own bank account, unfortunately, the funds cannot be returned. However, you can still use the credited amount for playing. Make sure to top up correctly by uploading the bank-in slip through (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). After submission, wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not appear within 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda tersalah transfer ke akaun bank sendiri, sayangnya wang tersebut tidak boleh dipulangkan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan jumlah yang telah dikreditkan untuk bermain. Pastikan anda top-up dengan betul dengan memuat naik slip bank-in melalui (WALLET â†’ TOPUP). Selepas penghantaran, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika kredit tidak muncul dalam 10 minit, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure it is processed correctly?

languages.en: What should I include when making an online transfer to ensure it is processed correctly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya sertakan semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian untuk memastikan ia diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: When making an online transfer, please ensure to fill in your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field along with other payment details. This is crucial for us to verify the receipt quickly.
detailed.ms: Semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian, sila pastikan untuk mengisi ID JOKER anda dalam ruangan 'Rujukan Penerima' bersama dengan butiran pembayaran lain. Ini sangat penting untuk kami mengesahkan resit dengan cepat.

question.text: Why hasn't my RM20 top-up been credited yet?
variations: saya DH topap 20 kenapa tak masuk lagi

languages.en: Why hasn't my RM20 top-up been credited yet?
languages.ms: Kenapa top-up RM20 saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: For your RM20 top-up, it usually takes 3-10 minutes for the system to process. If it still hasn't been credited after that, please contact live chat support with your complete receipt. They will be able to assist you more quickly. Don't worry!
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up RM20 anda, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses. Jika selepas itu masih belum masuk, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda. Mereka akan dapat membantu anda dengan lebih cepat. Jangan risau!

question.text: What does it mean if the status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What does it mean if the status shows PENDING in the system?

detailed.en: If the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: Why can't I deposit money from someone else's account?

languages.en: Why can't I deposit money from someone else's account?
languages.ms: Kenapa untuk nak masuk duit tak boleh dari ACC orang lain?

detailed.en: Deposits from someone else's account cannot be accepted due to security and verification reasons. All deposits must come from your own account to ensure there is no fraud. Therefore, if someone else wants to help, they need to make the deposit from their own account.
detailed.ms: Deposit dari akaun orang lain tidak boleh diterima kerana ia melibatkan keselamatan dan pengesahan. Semua deposit mesti datang dari akaun anda sendiri untuk memastikan tiada penipuan.

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai akaun saya dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit ke halaman tambah nilai dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk pengesahan segera.

question.text: What should I do if I forgot to write my JOKER ID during the transfer?
variations: I forgot to include my JOKER ID.
What happens if I don't enter my JOKER ID?

languages.en: What should I do if I forgot to write my JOKER ID during the transfer?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya terlupa untuk menulis ID JOKER semasa pemindahan?

detailed.en: If you forgot to enter your JOKER ID during the transfer, please upload your transaction receipt through the top-up page. Ensure that the receipt is complete and clearly shows the transaction details. For future transactions, make sure to enter the correct JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field to help the system process your top-up quickly. If you have any other issues, feel free to contact our live chat support.
detailed.ms: Jika anda terlupa memasukkan ID JOKER semasa transfer, sila muat naik resit transaksi anda melalui halaman top-up. Pastikan resit tersebut lengkap dan jelas menunjukkan butiran transaksi. Untuk transaksi akan datang, pastikan anda memasukkan ID JOKER yang betul di dalam ruangan 'Recipient Reference' untuk membantu sistem memproses top-up anda dengan cepat. Jika ada masalah lain, jangan ragu untuk hubungi sokongan live chat kami.

question.text: I would like to ask about the points that will be received after downloading the app. Will I definitely get them?

languages.en: I would like to ask about the points that will be received after downloading the app. Will I definitely get them?
languages.ms: Saya ingin bertanya tentang mata yang akan diterima selepas memuat turun aplikasi. Adakah saya pasti akan mendapatnya?

detailed.en: After downloading the app, points will usually be credited once you meet certain conditions. Make sure to check the relevant terms and conditions. If you have any further questions, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Selepas memuat turun aplikasi, mata biasanya akan dikreditkan setelah anda memenuhi syarat tertentu. Pastikan anda semak terma dan syarat yang berkaitan. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang ingin ditanya, jangan segan untuk tanya!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account after a top-up?
variations: What to do if winnings are not showing up?
How long does it take for winnings to be credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account after a top-up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya selepas topup?

detailed.en: If your winnings have not been credited after 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of the receipt to us. We will investigate immediately. Additionally, ensure that the receipt has been uploaded to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it still hasn't appeared after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan anda masih belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit kepada kami. Kami akan menyiasat dengan segera. Selain itu, pastikan resit telah dimuat naik ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi. Selepas memuat naik, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia masih belum muncul selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

detailed.ms: Jika anda telah mendeposit RM15 dan ia belum dikreditkan ke dompet anda, sila semak resit transaksi anda untuk memastikan semua maklumat adalah betul. Jika anda masih menghadapi masalah, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: How can I obtain a full receipt using Maybank?

languages.en: How can I obtain a full receipt using Maybank?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh mendapatkan resit penuh menggunakan Maybank?

detailed.en: To obtain a full receipt using Maybank, please follow these steps: 1. Tap on 'Accounts'. 2. Select your bank account. 3. Tap on 'View Receipts'. 4. Click the download button as shown in the image. Ensure that the receipt you send is complete as per the example below. If you encounter any issues, please contact us via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk mendapatkan resit penuh menggunakan Maybank, sila ikut langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Tekan 'Accounts'. 2. Pilih akaun bank anda. 3. Tekan 'View Receipts'. 4. Klik butang muat turun seperti yang ditunjukkan dalam gambar. Pastikan resit yang anda hantar lengkap seperti contoh di bawah. Jika anda menghadapi sebarang masalah, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Saya ingin tahu tentang cara deposit menggunakan Bank Rakyat dan jenis akaun yang perlu dipilih.
variations: Saya nk deposit
Pakai bank rakyat
Bank rakyat
Akaun saving ke atau lain

detailed.en: To deposit using Bank Rakyat, you can follow these steps: 1. Open the app and go to the 'Wallet' section. 2. Select 'Deposit'. 3. Choose Bank Rakyat as your bank option. 4. Enter the amount you wish to deposit. 5. Follow the instructions provided to complete the transaction. If you are asked to choose an account type, select 'Savings Account'. Ensure that the account holder's name matches the registered profile. If you encounter any issues, please contact our live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk deposit menggunakan Bank Rakyat, anda boleh ikut langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Buka aplikasi dan pergi ke bahagian 'Wallet'. 2. Pilih 'Deposit'. 3. Pilih Bank Rakyat sebagai pilihan bank anda. 4. Masukkan jumlah yang ingin anda depositkan. 5. Ikuti arahan yang diberikan untuk menyelesaikan transaksi. Jika anda diminta untuk memilih jenis akaun, pilih 'Akaun Simpanan'. Pastikan nama pemilik akaun sepadan dengan profil yang didaftarkan. Jika ada masalah, sila hubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What are the rules regarding deposits, bonuses, and transfers between IDs in relation to betting?

languages.en: What are the rules regarding deposits, bonuses, and transfers between IDs in relation to betting?
languages.ms: Apakah peraturan mengenai deposit, bonus, dan pemindahan antara ID berkaitan dengan pertaruhan?

detailed.en: Deposits, bonuses, and transfers between IDs can only be used for betting purposes. Full withdrawals can only be made after winning more than 30% of the deposit.
